NK101(de)006:1: // thugs sgrub yang tig gces sgron khrid kyi zin bris gzhung don rab gsal zhes bya ba bzhugs so //
NK101(de)006:3: rgyal ba kun dngos o rgyan rdo rje 'chang //
NK101(de)006:4: bde gshegs kun 'dus drag po rtsal gyi skur //
NK101(de)006:5: rab 'byams rgyal ba'i dkyil 'khor yongs s+dzogs pa //
NK101(de)006:6: rigs bdag bla ma dbyer med der phyag 'tshal //
NK101(de)006:7: thugs sgrub yang tig gces sgron gyi //
NK101(de)006:8: zab khrid nyams su len pa'i tshul //
NK101(de)006:9: brgyud ldan bla ma'i gsung ji bzhin //
NK101(de)006:10: zin bris gzhung don rab gsal ba //
NK101(de)006:11: khyab bdag rigs kyi bdag po mchog /
NK101(de)006:12: zur chen rdo rje 'chang chen po'i //
NK101(de)006:13: gsung las ji ltar thos pa bzhin //
NK101(de)006:14: bsre lhad med par 'dir bshad bya //
NK101(de)006:15: de la 'dir yang tig gces pa'i sgron me zhes
NK101(de)006:16: bya drag po thugs kyi bsgrub pa'i thems can rtsa
NK101(de)006:17: ba'i chos tshan nyer lnga las nyer gnyis pa /
NK101(de)006:18: o rgyan gyi slob dpon chen po dus gsum mkhyen pa pad+ma 'byung gnas la /
NK101(de)006:19: las can dag pa'i 'khor rnam pa lngas gsol ba btab pa la brten nas /
NK101(de)006:20: gsang ba rin chen 'dus pa sku'i tshab dang //
NK101(de)006:21: yang tig dpa' bo 'bru gcig gsung gi tshab //
NK101(de)006:22: pad+ma'i yang tig gces sgron thugs kyi tshab //
NK101(de)006:23: mkha' 'gro gsang ba'i sgrub thabs yon tan gyi tshab /
NK101(de)006:24: gdul bya las sbyor gyi gnad tig thems dang bcas
NK101(de)006:25: pa 'phrin las kyi tshab tu bzhag pa las 'dir
NK101(de)006:26: thugs kyi tshab tu bzhag pa yang tig gces pa'i
NK101(de)006:27: sgron me 'di gang bshad par bya ba'i chos yin
NK101(de)006:28: no // de yang gang las byung pa'i brgyud pa dang brgyud pa de las /
NK101(de)006:29: byung pa'i gdams ngag bshad pa ste spyi don gnyis pas /
NK101(de)006:30: dang po gang las byung ba'i brgyud pa ni /
NK101(de)006:31: spyir byang gter la sras brgyud slob brgyud yum brgyud gsum las /
NK101(de)006:32: 'di sras slob gnyis ka thun mong ba yin /
NK101(de)006:33: de yang spyir snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi ring lugs la /
NK101(de)006:34: rgyal ba rig 'dzin gang zag gsum //
NK101(de)006:35: dgongs pa rig pa rna bar brgyud //
NK101(de)006:36: gang la thug gi bar du 'o //
NK101(de)006:37: zhes gsungs pa ltar bshad tshul rgya che yang mdor bsdus te 'chad pa la /
NK101(de)006:38: 'og min chos kyi dbyings su chos sku kun bzang
NK101(de)006:39: gdod ma'i mgon po che mchog he ru ka'i skur
NK101(de)006:40: snang ba rang snang tshom bu'i dkyil 'khor nyid las
NK101(de)006:41: gzhan du ma gyur pa longs sku rgyal ba rigs
NK101(de)006:42: lnga la dgongs pa rang shar bas dgongs brgyud /
NK101(de)006:43: lcang lo can du sprul sku gsang ba'i bdag po
NK101(de)006:44: phyag na rdo rje dang smug nag dbang gi mkha'
NK101(de)006:45: 'gro la dgongs pas byin gyis brlabs te /
NK101(de)006:46: ri ma la ya'i rtser rigs can gra ma lnga
NK101(de)006:47: la bshad pa sogs rigs 'dzin rigs brgyud dam brda'
NK101(de)006:48: brgyud / de man chad la snyan brgyud dang /
NK101(de)006:49: gter ma'i phyogs la de'i steng du /
NK101(de)006:52: mkha' 'gro gtad rgya'i brgyud pa sogs kyi 'chad tshul mang bas /
NK101(de)006:53: 'dir thar chags su bkod na smug nag d+aa kis tshangs pa gdong gsum la /
NK101(de)006:54: de yang gzugs khams kyi tshangs pa gdong bzhi pa
NK101(de)006:55: dang mi 'dra bas 'dod khams kyi ri rgyal lhun
NK101(de)006:56: po'i rtse mor 'khod pa tshangs pa gdong gsum pa
NK101(de)006:59: za hor gyi rgyal po dzah mkhas pa sh+aakya pra b+ha wa /
NK101(de)006:60: o rgyan dus gsum mkhyen pa pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK101(de)006:61: pan chen bi ma la mi tra /
NK101(de)006:64: sna nam rdo rje bdud 'joms sogs dang /
NK101(de)006:65: 'di rnams kyi lo rgyus rnam thar snga 'gyur bka'
NK101(de)006:66: gter la grags che ba ltar yin pas 'dir ma
NK101(de)006:67: bkod la / gter bton rig 'dzin chen po rgod
NK101(de)006:68: ldem can dngos grub rgyal mtshan zhabs ni ri khrod
NK101(de)006:69: pa bzang po grogs pa'i kha byang dang /
NK101(de)006:70: ri bo bkra bzang nas gter gyi lde mig la brten nas /
NK101(de)006:71: byang zang zang lha brag gi sked brag ri dug
NK101(de)006:72: sbrul spungs 'dra nas mdzod lnga'i gter chen gdan drangs
NK101(de)006:73: pa'i gter mdzod re re la yang chos tshan brgya
NK101(de)006:74: phrag re bzhugs pas na lnga brgya phrag gcig tu
NK101(de)006:75: grags shing / drag po thugs kyi bsgrub pa'i skor
NK101(de)006:76: 'di lho phyogs gser mdzod ser po nas phal cher
NK101(de)006:78: de ltar gter bton chen po dang sku sras rnam
NK101(de)006:79: rgyal mgon po ste yab sras gnyis kas rjes su
NK101(de)006:80: bzung ba'i lung zin gyi slob ma rig 'dzin sangs
NK101(de)006:82: des se ston nyi ma bzang po la gnang zhing /
NK101(de)006:83: 'di nyid ni gter bton gyi dngos slob yin cing /
NK101(de)006:84: de yang se ston gong ma dag gis glang la
NK101(de)006:85: khal bkal zhing sgrub gnas btsal bas sa der glang
NK101(de)006:86: nyal ba la dbyug pa brgyas bsnun kyang ma langs
NK101(de)006:87: par mkhar te nyal bas de khar gnas gzhi bting
NK101(de)006:88: ba la / dpal ldan brgya mkhar gsang sngags gling du grags pa'i gnas der /
NK101(de)006:89: se ston nyi ma bzang pos tho rengs kyi skabs
NK101(de)006:90: shig thugs sgrub kyi 'phrin las mdzad pas ting 'dzin
NK101(de)006:91: rtse gcig tu song ba'i mthar cung zad mnal bar
NK101(de)006:93: khyad par sngags srung e ka dz+aa tis sku lus
NK101(de)006:94: bor ma thag o rgyan chen po'i zhabs drung du
NK101(de)006:95: byon te lung bstan thob nas /
NK101(de)006:96: steng phyogs 'khor ba zil gnon gyi zhing du bsgrod
NK101(de)006:97: cing sems can 'bum phrag bdun grol bar lung bstan
NK101(de)006:98: pa yin no // des se ston mgon po bzang po la gnang /
NK101(de)006:99: 'di yang bsgrub pa mthar phyin du sku tshe dril
NK101(de)006:100: bas spangs rtogs kyi yon tan dang ldan pa zhig
NK101(de)006:101: go // brgyud 'debs kyi dpe rgyun 'gar se ston
NK101(de)006:102: mgon po bzang po sngon dang nyi bzang rjes su
NK101(de)006:103: bris pa nor bar shes dgos so //
NK101(de)006:104: des se ston rin chen rgyal mtshan la gnang bas
NK101(de)006:105: 'di nyid ni mkhas grub chen por bzhugs shing dam
NK101(de)006:106: pa du ma'i zhabs pad bsten pas lung rtogs kyi
NK101(de)006:107: yon tan du mas phyug pa'i 'chad rtsom mang du
NK101(de)006:108: mdzad pas snga 'gyur bka' gter gyi bstan pa'i srol
NK101(de)006:110: des spyan tshab mgon po zla ba la gnang bas
NK101(de)006:111: 'di nyid ni mngon s+dzogs ma mo la grub pa
NK101(de)006:112: brnyes shing / sa dam gyi ri khrod du bsgrub pa snying por mdzad pa zhig go //
NK101(de)006:113: des mnyam med nub dgon pa byams pa chos rgyal mtshan la gnang bas /
NK101(de)006:114: dam pa 'di ni bstan pa yongs s+dzogs kyi bshes
NK101(de)006:115: gnyen mkhas grub chen po gshin rje tshe bdag dang
NK101(de)006:116: pad+ma yang gsang las grub pa bsnyes pa sum ldan
NK101(de)006:117: rdo rje 'dzin pa chen po yin la /
NK101(de)006:118: skabs shig 'jig rten du mi dge ba'i ltas skar
NK101(de)006:119: ma phod can shar ba la gshin rje'i gtor zor
NK101(de)006:120: 'phangs pas mi snang bar gyur pa sogs nus mthu
NK101(de)006:121: mnga' ba dang / zhing khams 'phos pa'i tshe ngo mtshar gyi rtags du ma dang /
NK101(de)006:122: sku gdung zhugs la phul ba'i tshe dud ris las
NK101(de)006:123: rta mgrin yang gsang gi sku shar ba sogs ngo
NK101(de)006:124: mtshar gyi rnam thar mtha' yas pa'o //
NK101(de)006:125: des thugs sras blo gros rgyal mtshan la gnang zhing /
NK101(de)006:126: 'di yang mnyam med nub dgon pa'i thugs sras dang
NK101(de)006:127: 'di skabs su snga 'gyur gyi bstan 'dzin chen po
NK101(de)006:128: rgyal mtshan gyi mtshan mtha' can brgyad byung ba'i nang
NK101(de)006:130: tshul khrims rnam par dag cing tshe bdag gi ljags bsnyen mdzad dus ya m+aan+ta ka'i zhal gzigs shing /
NK101(de)006:131: mgon po legs ldan bran du 'khol ba byang bdag
NK101(de)006:132: po dpon g.yog la tshe dbang mdzad dus tshe ril
NK101(de)006:133: zad pa la ljags phu btab cing phyag gis reg
NK101(de)006:134: pas mngon sum du 'phel ba'i grub mtshan byung zhing
NK101(de)006:135: mnyam med rje'i gdan sar bzhugs pa zhig go //
NK101(de)006:136: des mkhan chen byams pa bzang po la gnang zhing /
NK101(de)006:137: 'di nyid ni bya rgod gshongs kyi dge bshes rdzogs
NK101(de)006:138: chen zang thal dang lam 'bras kyi rnal 'byor mthar
NK101(de)006:139: phyin pa ngam rings dga' ldan byams pa'i gling gi
NK101(de)006:140: mkhan sar bzhugs pa yin no //
NK101(de)006:141: des kun bzang chos kyi nyi ma la gnang zhing /
NK101(de)006:142: 'di ni grub brnyes sbas pa'i rnal 'byor pa zhig
NK101(de)006:143: yin pa ha cang grags mi che bas rnam thar
NK101(de)006:145: des rig 'dzin 'brug sgra bzang po la gnang /
NK101(de)006:146: 'di ni srid gsum rnam rgyal gyi dge bshes /
NK101(de)006:147: kun mkhyen chen po'i bstan bcos gsang 'grel phyogs bcu mun sel thugs la tshud cing /
NK101(de)006:148: dam pa sangs rgyas kyi rnam sprul du gter lung gis zin pa /
NK101(de)006:149: rdzogs chen zang thal gtso bor gyur pa'i bka' gter
NK101(de)006:150: gyi zab chos mang du bzhugs pa rdzogs chen gyi
NK101(de)006:151: 'chad nyan gtso bor mdzad pas rong pa rdzogs chen
NK101(de)006:152: par grags shing lha btsun nam mkha' 'jigs med sogs
NK101(de)006:153: bstan 'dzin gyi slob bu mang du bskrun pa zhig
NK101(de)006:154: go // des rig 'dzin 'phrin las lhun grub la
NK101(de)006:155: gnang zhing dam pa 'di nyid ni gnyos rigs su
NK101(de)006:156: go // sku bltams shing / mkhas grub mdo sngags
NK101(de)006:157: bstan 'dzin sogs skyes chen du mar gsar rnying bka'
NK101(de)006:158: gter gyi dam chos mang du gsan cing /
NK101(de)006:159: phyis snga 'gyur gyi bstan 'dzin khrod na gsan rgya
NK101(de)006:160: che bar rgyal dbang thams cad mkhyen pa chen po
NK101(de)006:161: lnga bas kyang basngagasa par mdzad cing /
NK101(de)006:162: gter lung las sangs rgyas ye shes kyi sprul par lung gis zin cing /
NK101(de)006:163: mkhas pa la grub pa'i yon tan gyis brgyan pa /
NK101(de)006:164: dag pa'i snang bar mkha' 'gro ma bde chen rgyal
NK101(de)006:165: mos mtshams sbyar te gu ru pad+mas zhal bstan cing
NK101(de)006:166: dbang bskur byin gyis brlabs pa rigs sras rtsod bral
NK101(de)006:167: gyi gter chen 'gyur med rdo rje'i yab rjer gyur
NK101(de)006:169: des kho bo'i bla ma zur chen rdo rje 'chang
NK101(de)006:170: chen po chos dbyings rang grol la gnang ba ste
NK101(de)006:171: / rig 'dzin mkhas grub chen po 'di nyid ni
NK101(de)006:172: gnyags dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra'i sprul par rig 'dzin
NK101(de)006:173: yol mo pa chen po'i zab gter dang lha btsun
NK101(de)006:174: rje'i dag snang rig 'dzin srog sgrub kyi chos bdag
NK101(de)006:175: / / rgyal dbang lnga pa'i dag snang rgya can skor sogs las gsal bar lung gis bstan cing /
NK101(de)006:176: zur rigs su sku bltams te 'khon ston dpal 'byor lhun grub /
NK101(de)006:178: rig 'dzin yol mo pa chen po /
NK101(de)006:179: ngag dbang ye shes grub pa /
NK101(de)006:180: yab rje 'khor lo'i dbang phyug gzhon nu don grub /
NK101(de)006:181: rgyal dbang thams cad mkhyen pa lnga pa chen po /
NK101(de)006:183: gsung sprul tshul khrims rdo rje /
NK101(de)006:184: dar sdings rig 'dzin 'phrin las lhun grub sogs gsar
NK101(de)006:185: rnying gi skyes chen du ma las zab pa dang
NK101(de)006:186: rgya che ba'i chos tshul mtha' yas par gsan cing
NK101(de)006:187: / zab chos kyi bdud rtsi phar yang rtsol ba /
NK101(de)006:188: thos don nyams su bzhes pa'i bsgrub pa mthar phyin
NK101(de)006:189: pa mdo sngags rig gnas sogs shes bya'i gnas mtha'
NK101(de)006:190: dag gzigs pa'i kun mkhyen sems can la brtse ba
NK101(de)006:191: snying rje chen pos gzigs shing phan pa kho na
NK101(de)006:192: lhur mdzad pa'i sems dpa' chen po mthu stobs nus
NK101(de)006:193: pa'i dbang phyug dkyil 'khor rgya mtsho'i khyab bdag tu
NK101(de)006:194: gyur pa snga 'gyur gyi bstan pa'i srog 'thud pa'i
NK101(de)006:195: bka' drin bla na med pa rtsol ba zhig yin
NK101(de)006:196: la / khyad par dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ra'i sngon gnas rjes dran gyi tshul ni /
NK101(de)006:197: yar klungs bkra shis rtser tshar lugs kyi zab chos rnams gsan par phebs zhor /
NK101(de)006:198: bsam yas bu tshal mjal bar phebs pas sngon gyi bag chags mang du sad cing /
NK101(de)006:199: khyad par du d+aa ril gyi sgra zhig gsan pa'i mod la mdun gyi nam mkhar /
NK101(de)006:200: slob dpon chen po pad+ma 'byung gnas /
NK101(de)006:201: g.yas su pan chen bi ma la /
NK101(de)006:202: g.yon du mkha' 'gro 'tsho rgyal rnams mngon sum du gzigs par /
NK101(de)006:203: gu ru zhi ba'i yan lag bcu pa mdzad cing dzahmh'u bam hoh zhes dbang bzhi blangs pas /
NK101(de)006:205: dz+ny+aa na ku m+aa ma yengs gson mdzod cig /
NK101(de)006:206: chos dbyings rnam dag ye grol gdod ma'i klong /
NK101(de)006:207: ngo bo rang bzhin thugs rje gsum dang ldan /
NK101(de)006:208: mi 'gyur gting zab brjod bral lhang nge ba /
NK101(de)006:209: dri bral yan pa lhun grub chos kyi sku /
NK101(de)006:212: 'khor 'das thams cad byang chub sems kyi dkyil /
NK101(de)006:213: gdod nas dag pa sku gsum lhun gyis grub /
NK101(de)006:214: de nyid ma bcos lcog bzhag so ma'i ngang /
NK101(de)006:215: ye grol dag pa de nyid nyams su longs /
NK101(de)006:217: 'tsho rgyal gyis yang dag don la skye 'chi gnyis med kyang /
NK101(de)006:218: gnas skabs sha khrag lus 'di nges par 'gyur /
NK101(de)006:219: tshe 'di'i snang ba rmi lam sgyu ma 'dra /
NK101(de)006:220: rang ngo shes nas skad cig brtan pa thob /
NK101(de)006:222: de zhor du 'jam mgon bka' 'gyur ba chen po dang /
NK101(de)006:223: rgyal dbang thams cad mkhyen pa chen po gnyis /
NK101(de)006:224: snyigs dus gsang sngags rdo rje theg pa'i bstan pa'i sgron mer lung bstan ma thag /
NK101(de)006:225: dpal mgon zhal bral gzugs can dngos su byon te /
NK101(de)006:226: rje bka' 'gyur ba chen po chos rgyal khri srong gi dus kha che'i pan chen d+harma p+aa la /
NK101(de)006:227: rgyal sras dngul chu chos rdzong pa tshar chen chos
NK101(de)006:228: kyi rgyal po sogs kyi skye brgyud du lung bstan
NK101(de)006:229: mdzad pa sogs ngo mtshar gyi gnas du ma dang
NK101(de)006:230: / gzhan yang dag pa'i gzigs snang mtha' yas shing /
NK101(de)006:231: rgyal dbang mchog gi ti sh+r+air gyur /
NK101(de)006:232: bstan 'dzin gyi skyes bu mang po smin grol gyi
NK101(de)006:233: lam la bkod pa sogs mdzad 'phrin rgya che zhing
NK101(de)006:234: / mthar gzugs sku chos dbyings su bsdus pa' tshe /
NK101(de)006:235: bsam yas mchims phu'i dur khrod du kho bos sku gdung zhugs la phul ba'i tshe /
NK101(de)006:236: nam mkha' 'jam sprin gyis khyab cing /
NK101(de)006:237: me tog gi char dang khyad par pur dud kyi
NK101(de)006:238: sne la 'od dkar po sder ma tsam zhig o
NK101(de)006:239: rgyan gsang phug tu 'ja' dkar zugs pa'i rtser song
NK101(de)006:240: ba dang / gu ru'i sprul pa bya rgod thang
NK101(de)006:241: dkar zhig nam mkha' la lding ba sogs kun gyis
NK101(de)006:242: mthong ba'i ngo mtshar bsam las 'das pa byung ba
NK101(de)006:243: ba dang / lags so // dam pa des bdag rjes su bzung ba yin te /
NK101(de)006:244: de yang rang lo drug pa nas bcu drug gi
NK101(de)006:245: bar du yang yang zhabs kyi pad+mora btud pa'i smin
NK101(de)006:246: grol gyi zab chos mang du nos shing /
NK101(de)006:247: khyad par rang lo bcu drug gi thog gung thang
NK101(de)006:248: gi gtsug lag khang gi yang rtser gsang 'grel pa
NK101(de)006:249: bkab / rong 'grel g.yu tig phyogs bcu mun sel
NK101(de)006:250: sogs 'grel pa bzhi'i lung dang rat+na'i 'dus pa skor
NK101(de)006:251: bzhi sogs zab chos mang du gnang zhing /
NK101(de)006:252: khyad par rdzogs chen dgongs pa zang thal ka dag
NK101(de)006:253: lhun grub kyi nyams khridakyi gzhung btsugs pa'i zur brgyan
NK101(de)006:254: du yang tig gces sgron dang /
NK101(de)006:256: rig 'dzin srog sgrub kyi khrid sogs smin par rtsal zhing zhabs pad yun ring du bsten /
NK101(de)006:257: mthar gsang ba rmad byung ma'i dbang khrid dang /
NK101(de)006:258: ma gcig gi spyod khrid kyi man+dala tsam du slebs la nged kyang cung zad bro 'tshal bas /
NK101(de)006:259: der chos mtshams gnang ba'i nged la bsun bzlog brtan
NK101(de)006:260: bzhugs sogs rgyas par rtsal zhing de'i phyi lo zhing
NK101(de)006:261: khams 'phos pa sogs rnam thar du gsal ba ltar
NK101(de)006:262: ro // rig 'dzin brgyud pa spel legs nor bu'i 'phreng /
NK101(de)006:263: sel med dgos 'dod re skong yid bzhin gyi /
NK101(de)006:264: smin grol 'dod dgur rtsol mdzad rtsa brgyud kyi /
NK101(de)006:265: yongs 'dzin dam pa rnams la phyag bgyi 'o //
NK101(de)006:267: spyi don gnyis pa brgyud pa de las byung ba'i gdams ngag dngos bshad pa la /
NK101(de)006:270: dbang ma thob par rgyud dang gdams ngag gi zab khrid 'chad par mi rung yang /
NK101(de)006:271: deng sang ras chod byed pa mang du snang bas /
NK101(de)006:272: des na thugs sgrub drag po rtsal gyi thems med
NK101(de)006:273: kyi dbang chog chen mo sgrub pa sde dgu dang
NK101(de)006:274: sbyar ba dang / thems can drug pa dbang bskur
NK101(de)006:275: 'bring po bsgrub pa sde drug dang 'brel ba dang
NK101(de)006:276: sbyar ba dang / / bsdus pa byin rlabs thugs
NK101(de)006:277: rje'i dbang lnga zhi drag thun mong gi gtor dbang
NK101(de)006:278: zangs mdzod ma sogs legs par thob pa'am /
NK101(de)006:279: khyad par dbang bskur che 'bring gnyis gang rigs kyis
NK101(de)006:280: smin par byas pa zhig la zab khrid ston par
NK101(de)006:282: gnyis pa grol byed kyi gdams ngag ji ltar ston tshul ni /
NK101(de)006:283: gtso bor gter gzhung gi zin po gtso che zhing khyad par nub dgon nas brgyud pa'i khrid rim /
NK101(de)006:285: rigs 'dzin 'phrin las lhun grub la gsan skabs su
NK101(de)006:286: mdzad pa dmigs rim gsal byed zin bris nyid rtsa
NK101(de)006:287: bar bzung ste 'chad par byed pa la /
NK101(de)006:289: thog mar sngon 'gro gzer lnga dmigs rim bcad /
NK101(de)006:290: ces gsungs pa'i dang po thun mong gi sngon 'gro gzer lnga ni /
NK101(de)006:291: byang gter spyi dang khyad par s+dzogs chen ka dag lhun grub /
NK101(de)006:292: thugs sgrub rnam gsum bcas pa'i sngon 'gror mdzad pas /
NK101(de)006:294: kun bzang thugs la phyag 'tshal lo zhes mchod par brjod nas /
NK101(de)006:295: dang po dad ldan skyes bu rnams zhes pa nas /
NK101(de)006:296: rin chen gnad kyi gzer lnga brtsams zhes pa'i bar
NK101(de)006:297: gyis lam nyams su len pa'i rnal 'byor pa bstan
NK101(de)006:298: / des ji ltar nyams su blang ba ni skyabs sems /
NK101(de)006:301: bla ma'i rnal 'byor te lnga po rang rgyud la
NK101(de)006:302: gzer btab pa bzhin dgos pas na gzer lnga zhes
NK101(de)006:303: so // de la dang po skyabs sems ni /
NK101(de)006:304: bdag dang khams gsum sems can rnams zhes pa nas /
NK101(de)006:305: thar bar bya phyir sems bskyed do zhes pa'i bar gyis lus mdor bstan nas /
NK101(de)006:306: gang la skyabs su 'gro ba'i yul ji ltar sgom pa ni /
NK101(de)006:307: bdag gi spyi bor nam mkha'i khams zhes pa nas /
NK101(de)006:308: bka' nyan las byed pho nyar bsam zhes pa'i bar gyis bstan pas /
NK101(de)006:309: de ltar sgom pa'i tshul ni rang gi spyi bor
NK101(de)006:310: pad sdong 'dab ma bzhi pa yangs shing rgya che
NK101(de)006:311: ba'i lte ba'i ze 'brur nyi zla'i gdan la rtsa
NK101(de)006:312: ba'i bla ma de nyid brgyud pa drug 'dus kyi
NK101(de)006:313: ngo bo rdo rje drag po rtsal yum phag mo
NK101(de)006:314: dang mnyam par sbyor ba bdag la dgyes zhal 'dzum
NK101(de)006:316: de'i mdun shar gyi 'dab ma dang shar phyogs kyi
NK101(de)006:317: steng 'og thams cad khyab par bdag cag gi ston
NK101(de)006:318: pa thub chen sh+aakya seng ge gtso bor gyur pa'i
NK101(de)006:319: theg dgu'i yi dam zhi khro rab 'byams kyi dkyil
NK101(de)006:320: 'khor lha tshogs ma tshang ba med pa'i sangs rgyas
NK101(de)006:321: dkon mchog dang / g.yas phyogs lho'i 'dab ma dang
NK101(de)006:322: nam mkha' steng 'og thams cad du bde bar gshegs
NK101(de)006:323: pa'i gsung rab glegs bam gyi rnam pa lung rtogs
NK101(de)006:324: kyi dam chos ma lus pa 'dus pa'i bdag nyid
NK101(de)006:325: dkon mchog dang / can / de'i bar mtshams thams
NK101(de)006:326: cad bee d+aur+ya'i gzhi la gser zhun mas bris pa
NK101(de)006:327: dang gser gyi gzhi la bee d+aur+ya'i khu bas bris
NK101(de)006:328: pa'i btags grol rgyud drug sogs kyis go mtshams med
NK101(de)006:329: par gtams pa te chos dkon mchog dang /
NK101(de)006:330: rgyab phyogs kyi 'dab ma dang steng 'og thams cad
NK101(de)006:331: rgyal ba rigs gsum mgon po dang rgyal tshab byams
NK101(de)006:332: pa mgon po sogs byang chub sems dpa'i dge 'dun
NK101(de)006:333: dang nyan rang sogs 'gro don mdzad pa'i dge 'dun
NK101(de)006:334: dkon mchog dang / g.yon phyogs kyi 'dab ma dang
NK101(de)006:335: steng 'og thams cad sngags kyi srung ma rdo rje
NK101(de)006:336: khro mo rag gdong ma gtso bor gyur pa'i mkha'
NK101(de)006:337: 'gro chos skyong bka' srung gter bdag dam can rgya
NK101(de)006:338: mtsho'i tshogs dang bcas pa ste 'di dag kyang dge
NK101(de)006:340: gang gis skyabs su 'gro mkhan ni /
NK101(de)006:341: rang nyid gtso bor gyur pa'i g.yas g.yon du pha ma /
NK101(de)006:342: 'og tu khams gsum rigs drug gis bsdus pa'i sems
NK101(de)006:343: can dgra gnyen bar ma'i tshogs thams cad mngon sum
NK101(de)006:344: lta bur 'khod pa la brtse ba snying rje chen
NK101(de)006:345: pos legs par brtags te rgyu mi dge ba dang
NK101(de)006:346: dkar nag sna tshogs kyi 'bras bu dngos su myong
NK101(de)006:347: ba 'di rnams la snying rje dang las bsags pa
NK101(de)006:348: la 'gyod sems drag pos skyabs su 'gro bar bya
NK101(de)006:349: dgos la / ji ltar skyabs su 'gro ba'i tshul ni /
NK101(de)006:350: rang gis byang drangs te mgrin gcig tu 'ur ding gis skyabs su 'gro bar dmigs te /
NK101(de)006:352: khams gsum 'khor bar 'khyams pa'i sems can kun zhes pa nas /
NK101(de)006:353: byang chub ma thob bar du thugs rjes gzigs zhes pa'i bar gyis spyir smos te bye brag tu /
NK101(de)006:354: yon tan kun 'byung dngos grub mchog gi gnas bla
NK101(de)006:355: ma rin po che la skyabs su mchi zhes brjod
NK101(de)006:356: pa'i tshe bla ma rdo rje drag po rtsal de
NK101(de)006:357: nyid la yid mig rlung gsum rtse gcig tu bstad
NK101(de)006:358: pa'i mos gus gdung shugs drag po ma yengs par
NK101(de)006:359: bya / de bzhin du gang la gang 'dul sogs
NK101(de)006:360: tshig rkang gnyis kyi dus shar gyi yi dam dang
NK101(de)006:361: bya / / sangs rgyas gsungs las sogs kyi dus lho'i chos dang /
NK101(de)006:362: thugs rje chen pos zhes sogs kyi skabs nub kyi dge 'dun dang /
NK101(de)006:363: gdul bya'i don du zhes sogs la byang gi chos
NK101(de)006:364: srung rnams la sems bstad de skyabs 'gro lan mang
NK101(de)006:365: du bya'o // skyabs yul de rnams la phyi nang
NK101(de)006:366: gsang ba de kho na nyid kyi rnam bshad sogs
NK101(de)006:367: mang du yod kyang yi ges 'jigs te brir ma
NK101(de)006:368: du bya'o // lang zhing / de dag kyang chos
NK101(de)006:369: skur bltas te skyabs su song na nges don gyi
NK101(de)006:371: longs skur bltas na sku dang zhing khams rgyas pa'i yon tan /
NK101(de)006:372: sprul skur bltas na sprul pas 'gro ba 'dren nus pa'i yon tan skye bar gsungs /
NK101(de)006:373: de dang rjes su 'brel bar sems bskyed pa ni /
NK101(de)006:374: spyir smon 'jug don dam sogs kyi bshad gzhi rnams btang snyoms su byas te /
NK101(de)006:375: gong gi skyabs yul de rnams sems bskyed blang ba'i yul dpang po lta bur bsgoms te /
NK101(de)006:376: sems can thams cad kyi don du bdag gis rdzogs
NK101(de)006:377: pa'i sangs rgyas kyi go 'phang thob par bya snyams
NK101(de)006:378: pa'i smon pa sems bskyed dang /
NK101(de)006:379: de'i phyir du lam gyi 'jug sgo mang yang /
NK101(de)006:380: zab gsang 'od gsal rdo rje snying po'i bskyed rdzogs
NK101(de)006:381: kyi lam zab mo 'dir 'jug cing nyams su blang
NK101(de)006:383: de'i phyiir bdag gis dus gsum du bsags pa'i dge tshogs kyi mthu las /
NK101(de)006:384: mkha' khyab kyi 'gro ba ma lus pa byang chub thob pa dang /
NK101(de)006:385: don dam par rang byung rig pa rang shar gyi
NK101(de)006:386: chos sku yang dag snying po rtogs par shog cig
NK101(de)006:387: pa'i don dam sems bskyed sogs gsal btab ste /
NK101(de)006:388: bdag gis dus gsum bsags pa'i dge ba yis zhes pa nas /
NK101(de)006:389: 'gro ba 'dren pa'i ded dpon byed par shog ces
NK101(de)006:390: pa'i bar lan mang du brjod cing skyabs sems snying
NK101(de)006:393: dbang po rab 'bring tha ma yis zhag gsum lnga'am
NK101(de)006:394: bdun gyi bar rim par skyabs 'gro sems bskyed bya
NK101(de)006:395: zhes gsungs pas nyams khrid kyi dus de ltar bya'o
NK101(de)006:396: // skyabs sems 'di rnams nyams su len skabs rgyu dang 'bras bu'i skyabs 'gro /
NK101(de)006:397: smon 'jug don dam bdag gzhan mnyam barje'i byang sems bsgom tshul /
NK101(de)006:398: phar phyin drug gi lam sogs la sgro 'dogs chod par bya ba ni shin tu gces so //
NK101(de)006:399: de ltar skyabs sems grub nas skyabs yul de rnams
NK101(de)006:400: kyi sku las 'od zer 'phros te rigs drug gi
NK101(de)006:401: sems can rnams la phog pas lus zag med bde
NK101(de)006:402: chen gyi sku dang sems rtog medachosa skur sangs rgyas
NK101(de)006:403: te bya ma bu 'phur ba bzhin du dag pa
NK101(de)006:404: mkha' spyod kyi gnas su 'ur ding gis 'phur bar
NK101(de)006:405: bsams / skyabs yul de rnams kyang 'od phung bde
NK101(de)006:406: ba chen po'i rang bzhin du gyur nas rang la
NK101(de)006:407: thim pas de rnams kyi sku gsung thugs dang rang
NK101(de)006:408: gi sgo gsum dbyer med du bsams la mnyam par
NK101(de)006:409: bsams / bzhag go / gnyis pa tshogs bsags pa ni /
NK101(de)006:411: ci yod longs spyod chags med dge bar thong zhes dang gzer lnga'i gzhung las /
NK101(de)006:412: gnyis pa bdag 'dzin 'grol ba ni bsod nams tshogs
NK101(de)006:413: gnyis bsag pa'i phyir zas dang longs spyod ci 'byor
NK101(de)006:414: ba 'phangs dang snying brtse thams cad kyang bde gshegs
NK101(de)006:415: mchod cing sbyin par btang dngos 'byor yid kyis rnam
NK101(de)006:416: sprul ba'i phyi nang gsang ba'i man+dala 'bul zhes gsungs
NK101(de)006:417: pa'i don / rgyu'i theg pa ltar grangs med gsum
NK101(de)006:418: du tshogs bsags pa'i ngal ba bsten mi dgos par
NK101(de)006:419: pa'i don / / 'bras bu'i theg pa 'dir bsod
NK101(de)006:420: nams dang ye shes kyi tshogs gnyis gsog tshul dngos
NK101(de)006:421: pa'i don / / zhen spang phyir / rang 'byor
NK101(de)006:422: ci yod chags med du mchod sbyin bya ba dang
NK101(de)006:423: khyad par phyi nang gsang ba'i man+dala gyi sgo nas
NK101(de)006:424: tshogs gnyis rdzogs pa'i zab lam dam pa nyams su
NK101(de)006:425: pa'i don / / zhen spang phyir / blang ba
NK101(de)006:426: ni / skyabs yul dang 'dra ba'i tshogs zhing de
NK101(de)006:427: dag rang gi mdun du dmigs la /
NK101(de)006:428: dang po spyi'i man+dala 'bul ba ni /
NK101(de)006:430: dbang chen gzhal yas dbus kyii lte ba la zhes pa nas /
NK101(de)006:431: yang dag snying po myur du rtogs par shog ces pa'i bar ngag tu brjod cing /
NK101(de)006:432: ji ltar dmigs tshul ni spyir dus 'khor mngon pa
NK101(de)006:433: sogs kyii 'dod tshul gyis snod bcud kyi 'jig rten
NK101(de)006:435: 'dir mngon pa ltar bsgom bde zhing gsar rnying thams cad de ltar mdzad pas /
NK101(de)006:436: stong gsum gyi stong chen po'i 'jig rten gyi khams
NK101(de)006:437: ri gling 'khor yug nyi zla lcags ri dang bcas
NK101(de)006:438: pa'i gnas tshul gyi don spyi nges par byas la
NK101(de)006:439: / snying thig rnams su lnga tshan lnga'i man+dala 'bul tshul rgyas par gsungs shing /
NK101(de)006:440: 'dir rang gi mdun du gser dngul 'khar ba sogs
NK101(de)006:441: kyi man+dala nas 'bras sogs kyi 'bru rnams sta gon
NK101(de)006:442: bya / de lta bu'i man+dala gyi tshom bu yang rgyas pa so bdun ma dang /
NK101(de)006:443: bsdus pa bdun ma sogs kyi bshad tshul dang /
NK101(de)006:444: gu ru pad+mas gsang sngags lam rim du /
NK101(de)006:445: bsgrub dang mchod pa'i man+dala gnyis su 'bul zhes gsungs
NK101(de)006:446: pa'i rang 'grel du bsgrub pa'i man+dala tshom bu lnga
NK101(de)006:448: tshom bu bdun ma mchod pa'i man+dala du bshad cing /
NK101(de)006:449: rdzogs chen sangs rgyas mnyam sbyor gyi sngon 'gro'i skabs dang /
NK101(de)006:450: 'dir yang mchod pa'i man+dala tshom bu bco lnga mar bshad pa ste /
NK101(de)006:451: ri rab gling bzhi gling phran brgyad /
NK101(de)006:452: nyi zla ste bco lngar bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)006:453: de lta bu'i tshom bu bkod pa dmigs rten tsam dang /
NK101(de)006:454: bsgom byar snod bcud kyi 'jig rten stong gsum gyi
NK101(de)006:455: stong chen po gling bzhi ri rab byed pa phrag
NK101(de)006:456: brgya nyi zla khor yug dang bcas par sprul te
NK101(de)006:457: 'bul dgos la / de lta bu'i man+dala de nyid
NK101(de)006:458: rang dbang du 'bul ba'i nus pa ma mchis kyang
NK101(de)006:459: 'bul dgos la / / bdag don du rgyal ba
NK101(de)006:460: rnams kyi thugs rje'i mthus bzhes par 'gyur ba yin
NK101(de)006:462: bdag gi don slad nyid kyi mthus bzhes shig /
NK101(de)006:464: khrid kyi dus skabs 'dir dngos 'byor gyi mchod pa yang ci nus su 'bul lo //
NK101(de)006:465: gnyis pa nang gi man+dala ni /
NK101(de)006:466: rang dbang du byas pa rnams blos blangs te 'bul ba yin pas /
NK101(de)006:469: 'jig rten las kyi 'dus pa'i bar do ru bdag
NK101(de)006:470: blos shin tu gces par gzung ba yi zhes pa
NK101(de)006:471: nas / dag pa ye shes rang gnas bstan du gsol zhes pa'i bar du ngag tu brjod cing /
NK101(de)006:473: skye 'chi'i bar do 'dir bdag gi blos gzung ba'i yul 'khor 'dod pa'i longs spyod /
NK101(de)006:474: pha ma bu tsha mdza' grogs zas nor gos rgyan
NK101(de)006:475: dang bcas pa gces 'dzin gyi blos gzung ba 'di
NK101(de)006:476: rnams blos lings kyis bskyur te 'bul bar dmigs so
NK101(de)006:477: // gsum pa gsang ba'i man+dala ni /
NK101(de)006:479: nang ltar gyi yul 'khor longs spyod dang bcas pa
NK101(de)006:480: 'di rnams bdag lus 'byung 'dus kyi nyer mkhor gyur
NK101(de)006:481: pas na / rgyu lus kyi phung po gces par
NK101(de)006:482: 'dzin pa 'di yang chags zhen med par 'bul ba
NK101(de)006:484: rang lus 'byung bzhi 'dus pa'i pho brang du zhes pa nas /
NK101(de)006:485: rang rig ye shes rtogs par mdzad du gsol zhes pa'i bar brjod cing 'bul tshul ni /
NK101(de)006:486: bla ma'i gsung rgyun ril por 'bul ba dang /
NK101(de)006:488: ril por 'bul na rang lus 'byung bzhi 'dus pa'i
NK101(de)006:489: pho brang gi dbus su tsit+ta rin po che 'bar
NK101(de)006:490: ba dang dbang po sgo lngas brgyan pa la rnam
NK101(de)006:491: shes tshogs brgyad 'khor gyi tshul du bskor ba /
NK101(de)006:492: sha khrag rus pa nang khrol dang bcas pa 'dod
NK101(de)006:493: yon sna tshogs dang mig gnyis nyi zla'i rnam par
NK101(de)006:495: lus kyi pags pa bshus te gser gyi sa gzhi'i dod dang /
NK101(de)006:496: khrag gis chag chag btab pa dri bzang gi chu
NK101(de)006:497: dang khog smad 'byung bzhi khog stod ri rab kyi
NK101(de)006:498: tshul la / mgo bo rnam par rgyal ba'i khang bzang /
NK101(de)006:500: yan lag nying lag sogs phyogs mtshams su gling bzhi gling phran gyi tshul du bkod cing /
NK101(de)006:501: sha khrag nang khrol sogs 'dod yon lnga'i rang bzhin
NK101(de)006:502: du chal par bkram te 'bul bar dmigs pa yin
NK101(de)006:503: gsung / de lta bu'i man+dala phyi nang gsang ba gsum gyi tshul du phul bas /
NK101(de)006:506: gsang ba sems kyi 'phro 'du thams cad bsod nams
NK101(de)006:507: dang ye shes kyi tshogs chen po rdzogs pa'i rgyud
NK101(de)006:508: 'gyur bas mchod pa gzhan las khyad par du 'phags
NK101(de)006:509: pa yin no // de ltar phyi nang gsang ba'i
NK101(de)006:510: man+dala rnams nyams khrid kyi dus su skyabs sems ltar
NK101(de)006:511: zhag grangs su bcad de 'bul zhing /
NK101(de)006:512: rgyun ldan ji ltar rigs par phul nas mchod yul rnams rang la bsdu'o //
NK101(de)006:515: gsum pa sgrib sbyong bshags pa'i gzer las kyi sgrib
NK101(de)006:516: pa ma dag par yang dag snying po mi rtogs
NK101(de)006:518: de nyid ji ltar nyams su blang ba ni /
NK101(de)006:519: rang gi sgyu lus bem po yi spyi bor pad+ma
NK101(de)006:520: nyi zla'i steng ahls rdo rje sems dpa' nyid ces
NK101(de)006:521: pa nas / phyi nang lus bkrus dag par bsam zhes pa'i bar ltar yiin la /
NK101(de)006:522: de la yang thun mong pa dang thun mong ma yin pa gnyis las /
NK101(de)006:523: thun mong ba ni gong gi dkyus ltar la /
NK101(de)006:524: thun mong ma yin pa ni /
NK101(de)006:526: rang gi spyi bor thun mong ba ltar gyi rdor
NK101(de)006:527: sems gsal ba de'i klad pa dung khang du gti
NK101(de)006:528: mug 'joms pa'i rdor sems dkar po /
NK101(de)006:529: mgrin par 'dod chags 'joms pa'i rdor sems dmar po /
NK101(de)006:530: thugs kar zhe sdang 'joms pa'i rdor sems mthing ga /
NK101(de)006:531: lte bar ser sna dang nga rgyal 'joms pa'i rdor sems ser po /
NK101(de)006:532: gsang gnas su phrag dog 'joms pa'i rdor sems ljang gu /
NK101(de)006:533: de rnams kyang pad zla'i gdan la sems skyil gyis
NK101(de)006:534: bzhugs pa'i so so'i thugs kar zla gdan la h'u
NK101(de)006:535: yig dkar dmar mthing ser ljang ba la yig brgya
NK101(de)006:536: sa bon gyi mdog ltar bskor ba gsal btab cing
NK101(de)006:537: / yig brgya bzla bzhin pas dung khang gi rdor
NK101(de)006:538: sems de'i thugs ka'i sa bon sngags 'phreng dang bcas
NK101(de)006:539: pa las 'od zer bdud rtsi dkar po'i rgyun babs
NK101(de)006:540: pas sku lus shel bum 'o mas gang ba ltar
NK101(de)006:541: gyur pa phyir lud de gzhi'i rdor sems de'i sku
NK101(de)006:542: lus kyang mer gyis gang ba zhabs g.yas pa'i mthe
NK101(de)006:543: bong nas 'dzags pas rang lus kyi phyi nang thams
NK101(de)006:544: cad sbyong byed 'od zer bdud rtsi dkar po'i rgyun
NK101(de)006:545: des bkrus pas sbyang gzhi gti mug gi las kyis
NK101(de)006:546: dud 'gror skye ba'i las sgrib sbyangs /
NK101(de)006:547: sbyang 'bras chos dbyings ye shes mngon du byas /
NK101(de)006:548: sbyong byed kyii 'od zer de phyogs bcur 'phros pas
NK101(de)006:549: sems can thams cad kyi sbyang gzhi sbyang 'bras sogs
NK101(de)006:551: de bzhin du mgrin pa'i rdor sems dmar po'i thugs
NK101(de)006:552: srog sngags 'phreng dang bcas pa las bdud rtsi dmar
NK101(de)006:553: po'i rgyun babs pas byu ru'i bum pa mtshal btul
NK101(de)006:554: ma'i khu bas khengs pa ltar gyur pa gzhi'i rdor
NK101(de)006:555: sems kyi sku lus shel bum mtshal gyi khu ba
NK101(de)006:556: lta bus gang ba zhabs mtheb nas 'dzags te /
NK101(de)006:557: sbyong byed 'od zer bdud rtsi des rang rgyud kyi
NK101(de)006:558: sbyang gzhi 'dod chags kyi dbang gis mir skye ba'i
NK101(de)006:559: las sbyangs / sbyang 'bras sor rtog ye shes dang
NK101(de)006:560: sems can gyi las sbyong byed sbyang gzhi sbyang 'bras
NK101(de)006:561: las sbyangs / gong ltar bsam / thugs ka'i rdor
NK101(de)006:562: sems mthing ga'i sa bon sngags 'phreng las sbyong byed
NK101(de)006:563: 'od zer bdud rtsi mthing ga'i rgyun byung ba bee
NK101(de)006:564: d+aur+ya'i bum pa mthing shun gyi khu bas gang ba
NK101(de)006:565: ltar gyur pa sogs gong ltar /
NK101(de)006:566: sbyang gzhi zhe sdang gis dmyal bar skye ba'i las sbyong zhing sbyang 'bras me long ye shes dang /
NK101(de)006:567: lte ba'i rdor sems kyi sa bon dang sngags 'phreng
NK101(de)006:568: las sbyong byed 'od zer bdud rtsi ser po'i rgyun
NK101(de)006:569: babs pas gser bum gser btul ma'i khu bas gang
NK101(de)006:571: sbyang gzhi ser sna dang nga rgyal gyis lha dang yi dwags su skye ba'i las sbyang /
NK101(de)006:572: sbyang 'bras mnyam nyid ye shes dang /
NK101(de)006:573: gsang gnas kyi rdor sems ljang gu'i sa bon sngags
NK101(de)006:574: 'phreng las sbyong byed 'od zer bdud rtsi ljang gu'i
NK101(de)006:575: rgyun byung bas mar gad kyi bum pa mar gad
NK101(de)006:576: kyi khu bas khengs pa ltar gang ba dang /
NK101(de)006:577: sbyang gzhi phrag dog gis lha min du skye ba'i las sbyangs /
NK101(de)006:578: sbyang 'bras bya grub ye shes mngon du gyur pa
NK101(de)006:579: sogs gong gi rigs 'gre sbyar te yig brgya bzla
NK101(de)006:581: thun bzhi thun drug gang bde bar yang snying gzungs dang bcas pa bzlas zhes gsungs pas yang snying /
NK101(de)006:584: he ru ka'i yig brgya sogs min pa'i rdo rje sems dpa'i yig brgya kho na bazla'o //
NK101(de)006:586: dbang po rab 'bring tha ma yis zhag gsum bdun
NK101(de)006:587: nam nyer gcig bar rim par sgrib sbyong ba la
NK101(de)006:589: khrid kyi dus zhag grangs de bzhin dang /
NK101(de)006:590: rgyun du bargya'am nyer gcig la nyung mtha' bya dgos te /
NK101(de)006:591: brgya rtsa bzlas na dus gsum gyi rgyal sras su 'gyur bar dong sprugs las gsungs shing /
NK101(de)006:592: nyer gcig bzlas na ltung ba mi 'phel bar bshad pa'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)006:594: phyi dang nang gi chus khrus bya /
NK101(de)006:595: rnal 'byor ma yi dbang yang bskur /
NK101(de)006:596: zhes pa'i rgyud lung dang sbyar ba'i rdor sems kyi
NK101(de)006:597: chu rgyun des lus nang gang ba'i nang khrus dbang
NK101(de)006:598: bzhi dang sbyor ba 'dug kyang 'dir gzhung dang zin
NK101(de)006:599: bris sogs la bshad tshod med do //
NK101(de)006:601: dung khang gi rdor sems 'od du zhu nas /
NK101(de)006:602: mgrin pa'i rdor sems la thim /
NK101(de)006:603: de thugs ka'i rdor sems la /
NK101(de)006:604: gsang gnas kyi rdor sems lte ba dang /
NK101(de)006:606: phyi'i rdor sems kyang thugs ka'i rdor sems dang /
NK101(de)006:607: de nyid 'od du zhu nas rang la thim pas /
NK101(de)006:608: rang gi sgo gsum gyi sdig sgrib bag chags dang
NK101(de)006:609: bcas pa dag nas bla ma rdo rje sems dpa'
NK101(de)006:610: dang rang sems dbyer med du gyur par bsams la
NK101(de)006:612: 'di ni thun mong ma yin pa'i zab gnad gsung rgyun ma yin pas rgyun par bsgoms na legs /
NK101(de)006:613: yang na rang rgyud la nyon mongs gang che brtags la /
NK101(de)006:614: gti mug shas che ba la dkar po /
NK101(de)006:617: ser sna dang nga rgyal la ser po /
NK101(de)006:618: phrag dog la ljang gu ste gang 'dul gyi sku so sor bsgom bzlas byed par yang gsungs so //
NK101(de)006:619: de yang gnyen po stobs bzhi'i sgo nas bshags bsdoms
NK101(de)006:620: byed dgos pas stobs bzhi ngos 'dzin pa gces so
NK101(de)006:621: // bzhi pa mi rtag bskul 'debs kyi gzer ni /
NK101(de)006:623: dang po mi rtag dran pas 'khor ba yi yul
NK101(de)006:624: 'khor longs spyo brtse gdung nye 'brel rnams gros btab
NK101(de)006:625: nan gyi 'khri ba rbad kyis bcad ces gsungs pa'i
NK101(de)006:627: bzhi pa bskul 'debs mi rtag gzer rang gi yul 'khor khang khyim dang zhes pa nas /
NK101(de)006:628: thun du bcad la mi rtag bsgom mi rtag mthong
NK101(de)006:629: nas chos la 'jug ces pa'i bar gyis bstan pa
NK101(de)006:630: ltar ngag tu brjod la sgom pa'i tshul ni /
NK101(de)006:635: 'khor ba'i nyes dmigs rnams thog mar sgom pa thun mong gi sngon 'gro dang /
NK101(de)006:636: skyabs sems sogs thun mong ma yin pa'i sngon 'gror byed kyang /
NK101(de)006:637: 'dir gzer lnga'i khongs su bsdus te gsungs pas /
NK101(de)006:639: rang gi yul 'khor khang khyim dang sa rdo ri
NK101(de)006:640: brag 'jig rten khams brtsig dang gnas dang 'jig pa
NK101(de)006:641: dang dus kyi 'pho 'gyur legs par bsam zhes sogs
NK101(de)006:642: kyis dang po phyi snod kyi 'jig rten mi rtag
NK101(de)006:644: bar du rang gi dgra dang gnyen srog chags kun
NK101(de)006:645: dang rang gi lus skye dang gson dang 'chi bar
NK101(de)006:646: bsam zhes sogs kyi gnyis pa rang gzhan skye 'chi'i
NK101(de)006:647: sdug bsngal / bcud kyi sems can mi rtag pa bsam pa dang /
NK101(de)006:648: tha ma 'khor ba rigs drug gi sdug bsngal rim
NK101(de)006:649: gyis brtag cing bsam zhes sogs kyis gsum pa rigs
NK101(de)006:650: drug gi sdug bsngal bsam pa sogs don gsum gyis
NK101(de)006:651: bstan pa ltar rgyas par 'chad cing bsgom du gzhug
NK101(de)006:652: dgos / 'di'i khongs nas dal 'byor rnyed dka' mi
NK101(de)006:653: rtag pa las 'bras 'khor ba'i sdug bsngal sogs gsung
NK101(de)006:654: rab spyi ltar rgyas par bshad de yid nges 'byung
NK101(de)006:655: dang skyo shas drag po bcos min du skye zhing
NK101(de)006:656: las 'bras la yid ches brtan po rnyed par bya
NK101(de)006:657: dgos / dgos so // lnga pa bla ma'i rnal 'byor ni gzer lnga'i gzhung las /
NK101(de)006:658: dus gsum bde gshegs thams cad kyis thugs rjes 'gro
NK101(de)006:659: ba'i don mdzad kyang bdag ni 'khor ba'i gnas su
NK101(de)006:660: 'khyams da lta nges pa'i don ston pa'i bla ma
NK101(de)006:661: de ni sangs rgyas kyi sprul pa yin te bka'
NK101(de)006:663: 'khor los bsgyur ba'i rgyal por yid bzhin gyi nor bu rtsol med du 'byung ba ltar /
NK101(de)006:664: dad ldan gyi mi la bla ma rtsol med du 'byung ba dang /
NK101(de)006:665: 'khor los bsgyur rgyal gshegs pa'i tshe /
NK101(de)006:666: nor bu yang rgya mtshor ldog pa ltar /
NK101(de)006:667: log lta can la bla ma de nyid dag zhing du gshegs pa'i dpe don dang bcas te /
NK101(de)006:668: bla ma'i rnal 'byor bsgom par bya zhes pa'i bar ngag tu brjod cing tshig rjes don dran bya /
NK101(de)006:669: bla ma'i rnal 'byor sgom tshul ni /
NK101(de)006:670: thugs sgrub rang gi chos sder logs su 'byung ba'i /
NK101(de)006:671: gsang mtshan thugs sgrub bla ma yi rnal 'byor pad+ma bdag gis bshad h'u /
NK101(de)006:672: rang lus der 'dzin med pa yi spyi bor pad+ma
NK101(de)006:673: nyi zla'i steng dar chen ltab khrid brtsegs pa'i gdan
NK101(de)006:674: de steng gu ru drag po rtsal zhes pas nas
NK101(de)006:675: / thugs ni drag po'i ngar dang ldan ces pa'i bar ltar ro //
NK101(de)006:676: de yang spyir bla ma khrom tshogs su sgom pa dang /
NK101(de)006:677: mtho brtsegs su sgom pa dang /
NK101(de)006:678: kun 'dus nor bu lugs su sgom pa gsum las /
NK101(de)006:679: 'dir kun 'dus nor bu lugs su sgom dgos te /
NK101(de)006:681: dus gsum sangs rgyas yi dam lha rnam dag brgyud
NK101(de)006:682: pa'i bla ma rnams bkrag mdangs 'od du mer re
NK101(de)006:683: re ma h+aa gu ru'i sku la 'dus kun 'dus
NK101(de)006:684: bla ma'i ngo bo la rtse gcig dad pas phyag
NK101(de)006:685: 'tshal lo gnyis med rol pa'i mchod pa 'bul sku
NK101(de)006:686: gsung thugs kyi dngos grub rtsol zhes gsungs pa'i phyir
NK101(de)006:687: / rang gi spyi bor rtsa ba'i bla ma de
NK101(de)006:688: nyid rdo rje drag po rtsal gyi sku'i rnam par
NK101(de)006:690: dus gsum gyi sangs rgyas yi dam zhi khro /
NK101(de)006:691: brgyud pa'i bla ma thams cad thugs ka'i 'od zer
NK101(de)006:692: gyis spyan drangs te bstim pas bkrag dang gzi mdangs
NK101(de)006:693: dang ldan par gyur nas mchog gsum rtsa gsum kun
NK101(de)006:694: 'dus kyii ngo bo de nyid la /
NK101(de)006:695: dad pas phyag 'tshal zhing dngos 'byor yid sprul gyi
NK101(de)006:696: mchod pa gnyis med rol pa chen por phul bas
NK101(de)006:697: sku gsung thugs kyi dngos grub thams cad rtsol bar
NK101(de)006:698: mos dgos shing / gzhung las kun 'dus nor bu
NK101(de)006:699: lugs su sgom pa gsal bar gsungs bzhin du bla
NK101(de)006:700: ma mtho brtsegs su sgom pa gzhung don dang 'gal
NK101(de)006:701: mos dgos shing / bar sems so // gsol ba 'debs pa ni /
NK101(de)006:703: 'og min chos kyi dbyings kyi pho brang du kun
NK101(de)006:704: bzang che mchog he ru ka la gsol ba 'debs
NK101(de)006:705: zhes pa nas / 'bad med lhun gyis grub par
NK101(de)006:706: mdzad du gsol zhes pa'i bar dkyus ltar la brgyud
NK101(de)006:707: tshul gter bton chen po nas /
NK101(de)006:708: rig 'dzin sangs rgyas byams bzang sogs brgyud 'debs bye brag pa ltar gsol 'debs rtse gcig tu bya'o //
NK101(de)006:709: mthar dbang bzhi blang ba sogs kyi spros pa mi dgos te /
NK101(de)006:711: bla ma 'od du mer gyis zhu bdag gi spyi
NK101(de)006:712: bor thim pa las tha mal lus 'di 'od du
NK101(de)006:713: zhu bdag gi lus ngag yid gsum po ma h+aa
NK101(de)006:714: gu ru'i ngo bor gyur rang rig bla ma'i ngang
NK101(de)006:715: der ni dar cig ma yengs glod la bzhag de
NK101(de)006:716: nas bla ma'i rnam par ldang thams cad sku gsum
NK101(de)006:717: bla mar blta zhes gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)006:718: bla ma rdo rje drag po rtsal de nyid bdag
NK101(de)006:719: la dgyes pa chen pos 'od du mer gyi zhu
NK101(de)006:720: nas / rang gi spyi bor thim pa la brten nas /
NK101(de)006:721: rang lus tha mal par snang ba 'di yang 'od
NK101(de)006:722: phung bde ba chen po'i rnam par zhu ste bdag
NK101(de)006:723: gi lus ngag yid gsum dang /
NK101(de)006:724: bla ma'i sku gsung thugs dbyer med rang rig bla ma drag po rtsal gyi ngo bor bsams la /
NK101(de)006:725: ma bcos pa'i ngang du lhod kyis glod la mnyam par bzhag /
NK101(de)006:726: rjes thob tu snang grag rig gsum thams cad sku
NK101(de)006:727: gsum bla ma'i rang bzhin du blta zhing gsal btab
NK101(de)006:728: po // de ltar thun mong gi sngon 'gro gzer lngas rgyud sbyang ba gal che ba yin te /
NK101(de)006:729: ka dag gi khrid gzhung las /
NK101(de)006:730: skyabs 'gro sems bskyed sngon du ma song na nang pa sangs rgyas kyi chos su mi 'gro bas /
NK101(de)006:731: ci byed skyabs 'gro sems bskyed kyis zin par bya
NK101(de)006:732: bdag 'dzin ma grol na rig pa'i mdangs mi 'char
NK101(de)006:733: bas / phyi nang gsang ba'i mchod pa 'bul lo
NK101(de)006:734: sgrib pa ma sbyangs na byang chub mi thob pas
NK101(de)006:735: sdig sbyong gi chos la nan tan bskyed rigs drug
NK101(de)006:736: gi sdug bsngal ma bsams na /
NK101(de)006:737: dge ba'i las la mi tshud pas 'khor ba'i sdug
NK101(de)006:738: bsngal la rtsis 'debs yang yang bya bla ma sangs
NK101(de)006:739: rgyas dngos su ma mthong na /
NK101(de)006:740: byin rlabs kyis rang rgyud 'grol ba dka' bas yon
NK101(de)006:741: tan bsams la bla ma'i rnal 'byor sgom zhes gsungs
NK101(de)006:742: pa'i phyir ro // gnyis pa thun mong ma yin pa'i sems 'dzin la gsum ste /
NK101(de)006:745: sems nyid phyag mtshan la sems 'dzin pa dang gsum las /
NK101(de)006:746: dang po ni zin bris rtsa ba las /
NK101(de)006:747: bla ma rang thim lus 'di lha ru gyur /
NK101(de)006:748: snang stong 'dzin med lha la sems 'dzin pa /
NK101(de)006:749: rags dang phra ba cha shas kun la 'dzin /
NK101(de)006:751: lus lha'i dkyil 'khor bsgom tshul ni gzhu las /
NK101(de)006:752: ma h+aa gu ru rdo rje drag po rtsal nga
NK101(de)006:753: yi sku tshab yin pas gsal bar bsgom zhes gsungs
NK101(de)006:754: pa ltar / skabs 'dir thugs sgrub rang gi gter
NK101(de)006:755: gzhung bdag bskyed zur du gsal ba 'dir blangs te
NK101(de)006:756: pa ltar / / bdag nyid kyis h'u h'u zhes
NK101(de)006:757: brjod pas skad cig dran rdzogs su ma h+aa gu
NK101(de)006:758: ru pad+ma 'byung gnas rdo rje drag po rtsal zhes
NK101(de)006:759: bya ba sku 'jigs pa'i cha lugs su bstan pa
NK101(de)006:760: gsung rngams pa'i nga ro sgrog pa thugs drag po'i
NK101(de)006:761: ngar dang ldan pa 'gying bag dang rol pa'i stabs
NK101(de)006:762: su bzhugs pa phyag g.yas gnam lcags kyi rdo rje
NK101(de)006:763: rtse dgu pa nam mkha' la 'phyar ba g.yon pa
NK101(de)006:764: gser gyi dril bu dku la bsten pa rus pa'i
NK101(de)006:765: rgyan drug dang rin po che'i dbu rgyan dang sbrul
NK101(de)006:766: gyi gdu bus brgyan pa khro gtum 'jigs pa'i gar
NK101(de)006:767: dgu dang ldan pa spyan gsum nyi zla 'khyil ba
NK101(de)006:768: ltar gzigs pa tshems gangs ri gtams pa ltar bzhad
NK101(de)006:769: pa ag tshom dus matha'i me ltar 'bar ba zhal
NK101(de)006:770: nas h'u gi sgra 'brug ltar sgrog pa za 'og
NK101(de)006:771: gi ber smug po dang dur khrod kyi chas brgyad
NK101(de)006:772: kyis brgyan pa dbu skra'i thor cog rus pas brgyan
NK101(de)006:773: pa zhabs gnyis stang stabs su bgrad de nyi zla
NK101(de)006:774: pad+ma'i gdan steng du rak+sha srin po pho mo bardzisa
NK101(de)006:775: pa'i gdan la bzhugs pa bskal pa'i me ltar 'bar
NK101(de)006:776: ba'i klong dkyil na 'gying bag tu brjid pa khams
NK101(de)006:777: gsum dbang du sdud cing srid gsum zil gyis gnon
NK101(de)006:778: pa'i bdag nyid can du gyur ces ngag tu brjod
NK101(de)006:780: de yang snang bzhin du stong ba /
NK101(de)006:781: stong bzhin du gsal bar 'char zhing /
NK101(de)006:782: 'dzin zhen med pa'i ngang la ci gnas su bzhag /
NK101(de)006:784: rags pa dang phra ba cha shas la sems 'dzin pa'i thog ma /
NK101(de)006:785: nga ni tha mal pa nam yang ma yin te /
NK101(de)006:786: rang rig lha skur shar ba rdo rje drag po
NK101(de)006:787: rtsal dngos yin snyams pa'i nga rgyal bzung ste sems
NK101(de)006:788: 'dzin / rags pa ni sku mdog mthing nag tu
NK101(de)006:789: 'bar ba 'jigs tshul can gsung drag po'i rngam sgra
NK101(de)006:790: 'dzin / can / thugs gdul bya gdug pa can
NK101(de)006:791: 'dul ba'i phyir du drag po'i ngar dang bcas pa
NK101(de)006:792: 'dzin / can / / sku 'gying bag dang rol pa'i stabs su bzhugs pa la sems 'dzin /
NK101(de)006:793: phra ba la gnyis te dang po rgyan can la sems 'dzin pa ni /
NK101(de)006:794: phyag g.yas gnam lcags kyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa 'phyar stabs su 'dzin pa /
NK101(de)006:795: g.yon pa gser gyi dril bu'i kha dkur bsten pa /
NK101(de)006:797: spyi bor dbu skra thor tshugs su bcings pa las
NK101(de)006:798: rus pa'i dra mig so gnyis 'phyang 'phrul 1dang bcas
NK101(de)006:799: pa / mgrin par rus pa'i dra mig bcu drug gi mgul 2rgyan /
NK101(de)006:800: rgyab mdun du se ral kha rus 'phreng nyis gshibs brgyad 3dang bcas pa /
NK101(de)006:801: sku smad stag sham gyi steng du rus pa'i dra mig re bzhi'i 'og 4pag /
NK101(de)006:802: phyag zhabs kyi mkhrig mar rus pa'i phyag gdub 5dang zhabs gsum 6ste rus rgyan drug /
NK101(de)006:803: skra mtshams su thod pa skam po lnga la rin
NK101(de)006:804: po che'i ze srog can rgyal ba rigs lngas mtshan
NK101(de)006:805: pa / sbrul rigs lngas dbu skra snyan mgul phyag zhabs do shal rnams spras pa /
NK101(de)006:806: snyan rgyan rin po che dang rus pa'i sna rgyan /
NK101(de)006:808: spyan gsum nyi zla ltar dra mig 'khyil zhing gzigs pa /
NK101(de)006:809: tshems 'phreng dang mche ba gangs ri ltar gtams pa bzhad cing h'u gi sgra 'brug ltar sgrog pa /
NK101(de)006:810: ag tshoms dang smin ma sma ra me ltar 'bar ba /
NK101(de)006:811: za 'og smug po'i ber phod lding thabs su gyon
NK101(de)006:812: pa'i steng du zhing glang gi pags pa gsol ba
NK101(de)006:813: / dpral bar thal chen gyi tshom bu /
NK101(de)006:814: mkhur tshos dang sna rtser rak+ta'i thig le /
NK101(de)006:815: lkog mar zhag gi zo ris /
NK101(de)006:816: thod pa skam rlon rnyid gsum mam yang na thod rlon gyi do shal can /
NK101(de)006:817: de yang thod pa skam po'i dbu rgyan dang thod rlon gyi do shal la gdags pa'i rgyan gnyis /
NK101(de)006:818: zhing glang stag lpags gsum la bgo ba'i gos gsum /
NK101(de)006:819: thal zhag rak+ta gsum la byug pa'i rtsi gsum ste dur khrod kyii chas brgyad du grags so //
NK101(de)006:820: deng sang bris 'bur phal cher la /
NK101(de)006:821: khro bo dkyus ma ltar dbu skra gzings pa kho na shas che yang /
NK101(de)006:822: 'dir dbu skra'i thor cog rus pas brgyan ces dang /
NK101(de)006:824: dbu skra'i thor tshugs nam mkha'i sprin ltar gtibs zhes gsungs pas /
NK101(de)006:825: dbu skra thor tshugs kho na'i rtser rdo rje phyed pa'i tog dang /
NK101(de)006:826: dbu skra'i lhag ma cung zad rgyab tu grol ba yin no //
NK101(de)006:828: rin chen 'bar bas dbu dang phyag zhabs spras zhes 'byung bas /
NK101(de)006:829: phyag zhabs kyi mkhrig ma dang phyag gi nywa gnyis su rin po che'i gdu bu can /
NK101(de)006:830: zhabs gnyis g.yas bskum g.yon brkyang gis srin po pho
NK101(de)006:831: kha sbub dang mo gan rkyal gyi steng du bgrad
NK101(de)006:832: pa de'i 'og tu nyi zla pad+ma'i gdan can ye
NK101(de)006:833: shes kyi me dpung rab tu 'bar ba'i dbus na
NK101(de)006:834: bzhugs pa / 'gying bag tu brjid cing khams gsum
NK101(de)006:835: dbang du sdud cing srid gsum zil gyis gnon pa'i
NK101(de)006:837: gnyis pa phra ba rgyan med la sems 'dzin pa ni /
NK101(de)006:838: sku mdog mthing nag bee d+aur+ya sngon po nyi ma'i 'od zer gyis cher 'bar ba lta bu dang /
NK101(de)006:839: spyan gsum dmar zlum 'khyil ba smin ma rdzi ma dang bcas te 'bar ba /
NK101(de)006:840: shangs khro gnyer dang ldan pa /
NK101(de)006:841: zhal gdangs pa he zhes bzhad pa lta bu /
NK101(de)006:842: sku lus sbom zhing gsus khyim che ba /
NK101(de)006:844: phyag zhabs kyi mthil bzhi khrag gis byugs pa ltar dmar ba /
NK101(de)006:845: sen mo rnams zangs mdog can bya sder ltar rno ba ste rgyan med la sems 'dzin no //
NK101(de)006:846: cha shas la sems 'dzin pa ni /
NK101(de)006:847: de dag kyang re re bzhin du gsal snang brtan por ma gyur gyi bar du sems 'dzin la /
NK101(de)006:848: de yang bying rmugs dang 'phro rgod kyi dbang du ma shor bar rnam pa gsal ba dang /
NK101(de)006:849: so so'i rnam dag dran pa dang /
NK101(de)006:850: nga rgyal brtan po reg mthong gi mtshan ma rnyed kyi bar du sems 'dzin no //
NK101(de)006:851: bskyed rim gyi sems 'dzin 'di gsal snang thon pa zhig nges par gal che bas /
NK101(de)006:852: lha sku snang la rang bzhin med pa me long
NK101(de)006:853: gi gzugs brnyan ltar rnam pa gsal bar 'char ba
NK101(de)006:855: gdos bcas kyi bem po bris 'bur gyi sku lta
NK101(de)006:856: bu'i bskyed rim nyag nyog dang der 'dzin gyi a
NK101(de)006:857: 'thas drag por zhen na ru trar gol ba sogs
NK101(de)006:858: bshad pas lam 'dir gcig tu brtson pas 'bad dgos
NK101(de)006:859: shing / rnam dag dran pa ni thems med kyi
NK101(de)006:860: rgyud yang gsang 'dus pa las rgya cher bshad pa
NK101(de)006:862: de ltar bskyed rim la goms pa'i nga rgyal brtan par bya dgos pas /
NK101(de)006:863: khrid kyi dus su shar bsgom ma yin pa'i rim
NK101(de)006:864: pa dang gcig car du res 'jog gi nyams len
NK101(de)006:865: thun du bcad la bsgom zhing thun mtshams su blo
NK101(de)006:866: bral gyi ngang du 'jog pa sogs rgyun bsring ngo
NK101(de)006:867: // de ltar lus lha la sems 'dzin pa song nas /
NK101(de)006:868: gnyis pa ngag sngags la sems 'dzin pa ngag sngags kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK101(de)006:870: de nas ngag nyid sngags la sems 'dzin pa /
NK101(de)006:871: yi ge h'u sngon snod bcud khyab pa ni /
NK101(de)006:872: kha dog sgra dbyibs kun la ci gnas bya /
NK101(de)006:874: rang gi mdun du h'u sngon po rang lus tsam zhig gsal bar dmigs nas de la sems 'dzin /
NK101(de)006:875: 'phro na h'u de las h'u grangs med pa 'phros
NK101(de)006:876: te phyi snod kyi 'jig rten dang nang bcud kyi
NK101(de)006:877: sems can thams cad h'u gis khyab par dmigs /
NK101(de)006:878: yang tshur bsdus te spro gzhi'i h'u sngon de la sems gzung /
NK101(de)006:879: de lta bu'i h'u kha dog sngon por snang ba dang /
NK101(de)006:880: dbyibs yi ge dbu chen gyi rnam pa h'u gi rang sgra sgrog pa rnams la sems 'dzin no //
NK101(de)006:882: yang tig dpa' bo 'bru gcig sngags kyi 'bru gsung
NK101(de)006:883: gi tshab yin rgyun chad med par zlos zhes gsungs
NK101(de)006:885: thugs sgrub la yi dam du bzung ba'i rgyun gyi bzlas brjod chag med du byed kyi yod na /
NK101(de)006:886: chos tshan nyer lnga las gsum pa gsang ba rin chen 'dus pa dang /
NK101(de)006:887: de'i gsal byed chos rgyal dbang po'i sdes mdzad pa dang /
NK101(de)006:888: nged kyi bris pa'i bsnyen pa'i yang yig zab don nor bu ltar /
NK101(de)006:889: h'u zhi ba shub bu brgya'i bar bdun phrag dang po'i dmigs pa dang /
NK101(de)006:890: drag po nyis rtsegs brgya'i bar bdun gnyis pa'i dmigs pa /
NK101(de)006:891: dbang lnga rtsegs brgya'i bar bdun gsum pa'i dmigs pa ste sum brgya dang /
NK101(de)006:892: rgyas pa bdun rtsegs nyer gcig bar bdun phrag bzhi
NK101(de)006:893: pa'i dmigs pa rnams sbyar ba'i sum brgya nyer gcig
NK101(de)006:895: khrid gzhung gi dgongs don rgyun chad med par bzla ba ni /
NK101(de)006:896: rlung 'byin 'jug thams cad h'u gi sgrar shes par byas te sems bzung na gzhung dang mthun /
NK101(de)006:897: skabs 'dir zin bris kha cig tu srung 'khor gzhal yas khang sogs phyi dkyil dang /
NK101(de)006:898: lus dkyil sgom tshul sogs bris 'dug kyang /
NK101(de)006:899: spyir dbang bskur sogs kyi skabs bdag bskyed thems can
NK101(de)006:900: bdun pa 'phrin las 'bring po ltar lus dkyil bsgoms
NK101(de)006:901: rjes / mdun bskyed kyi tshul du thems med dkyil
NK101(de)006:902: 'khor la brten nas bsgrub pa chen po zur nas
NK101(de)006:904: spyan 'dren mchod bstod sogs lhan gcig tu byed pa phyag gzhes su yod cing /
NK101(de)006:905: gzhan du na bsnyen pa'i skabs kyang /
NK101(de)006:906: dkyil 'khor gsum gyi bsgrub pa bya zhes gong du smos pa ltar lus lha'i dkyil 'khor /
NK101(de)006:908: sems chos nyid kyi dkyil 'khor las gzhan pa'i phyi dkyil la brten mi dgos shing /
NK101(de)006:909: srung 'khor bye brag pa zab khyad can yang logs
NK101(de)006:910: su yod pas 'dir bsre lhad kyi rgyas 'gebs mang
NK101(de)006:911: po ngal ba'i rgyur zad pas mi bya'o //
NK101(de)006:912: gsum pa thugs phyag mtshan la sems 'dzin pa ni /
NK101(de)006:914: sems nyid phyag mtshan gnam lcags rdo rje la /
NK101(de)006:915: 'dzin tshul snying dbus gnam lcags rtse dgur gyur //
NK101(de)006:916: de la spro bsdu gong bzhin 'dzin par bya /
NK101(de)006:917: zhes gsungs pa sgom tshul ni /
NK101(de)006:918: rang lhar gsal ba'i snying dbus gnam lcags kyi rdo rje rtse dgu pa zhig la sems bzung /
NK101(de)006:919: 'phro na de las rdo rje rtse dgu pa bsam
NK101(de)006:920: gyis mi khyab pa spros te phyi snod nang bcud
NK101(de)006:921: thams cad mer gyis gang bar mos /
NK101(de)006:922: yang tshur bsdus te snying dbus kyi spro gzhi'i rdo
NK101(de)006:923: rje la thim par bsams la mnyam par 'jog /'di
NK101(de)006:924: ni rtsa bar rdo rje dbus su bsgom pa de
NK101(de)006:925: las spro bsdu byed par gsungs pas de bzhin dang
NK101(de)006:926: / h'u gi sems 'dzin skabs mdun du h'u yig las spro bsdu byed pa las /
NK101(de)006:927: snying dbus nas spro ba'i gsal kha med pas 'di bzhin ma 'dres par bya'o //
NK101(de)006:929: gang zag dbang po rab 'bring tha ma yis bdun
NK101(de)006:930: dang bdun gnyis bdun gsum nyer gcig gis yon tan
NK101(de)006:931: rtags kyi dngos grub nges par 'byung longs spyod mtha'
NK101(de)006:932: rgyas tshogs kyi 'khor lo bskor ces gsungs pas nyams
NK101(de)006:933: khrid kyi dus sku gsung thugs kyi sems 'dzin zhag
NK101(de)006:934: grangs de lta bus rtags thon gyi bar du 'bad
NK101(de)006:935: cing / skabs 'dir spro na 'phrin gzhung gyer zhing
NK101(de)006:936: tshogs 'khor sogs bgyis na khrid gzhung dang mthun cing
NK101(de)006:937: cing / / ma byung yang 'gal ba med do //
NK101(de)006:939: de nas ka dag sngon 'gro rdo rje dang /
NK101(de)006:940: h'u sngon thig le dkar dmar dmigs rim skyong /
NK101(de)006:941: zhes pa'i sems 'dzin don gsum gyi dang po rdo
NK101(de)006:942: rje dkar po la sems 'dzin pa ni rdzogs chen
NK101(de)006:943: ka dag gi khrid yig gter gzhung ma rig mun
NK101(de)006:944: sel sgron me'i / snying po bcud bsdus lam gyi gnad khrid las /
NK101(de)006:945: tshe 'dir sangs rgyas bsgrub 'dod na phyi ltar yul
NK101(de)006:946: gyi snang ba la nang ltar rig pa'i brda ngo
NK101(de)006:947: sprod las can skal bar ldan pa yis mdun du
NK101(de)006:948: khru bdun bcal ba'i sar rdo rje dkar po rtse
NK101(de)006:949: lnga pa g.yas su 'khyir ba rang gzugs tsam gsal
NK101(de)006:950: bar bsgoms la drag por bskor ces gsungs pas rang
NK101(de)006:951: gi mdun nas khru bdun tsam gyi sar /
NK101(de)006:952: rdo rje dkar po rtse lnga pa rang gzugs tsam
NK101(de)006:953: zhig gsal btab la rdo rje de g.yas su 'khyil
NK101(de)006:954: li li 'khor ba la sems bzung /
NK101(de)006:955: de la dmigs pa gsal thebs pa'i rtags ni /
NK101(de)006:957: dmigs pa gsal thebs rtags 'di 'byung mgo 'khor rna
NK101(de)006:958: ba 'ur ba dang rlung rig gar bstad rdo rje
NK101(de)006:959: 'khyir zhes gsungs pas de ltar byung na log gnon
NK101(de)006:960: du rdo rje g.yon du 'khor ba la sems bstad
NK101(de)006:961: / mthar rlung sems rdo rje dbyer med du mnyam par 'jog cing /
NK101(de)006:962: de lta bu bdun gsum nyer gcig gang rigs su bsgoms pa'i mthar /
NK101(de)006:963: de nas zhag gcig dal bar bya zhes gsungs pas /
NK101(de)006:964: dmigs pa des sun pa ltar snang na /
NK101(de)006:965: zhag gcig gi ring dmigs pa'i spro bsdu bor nas gnas lugs kyi ngang nas ngal gaso'o //
NK101(de)006:966: gnyis pa h'u sngon po la sems 'dzin pa ni /
NK101(de)006:967: ka dag gi khrid gzhung las /
NK101(de)006:968: mdun du khru bdun bcal ba'i sar h'u chen sngon
NK101(de)006:969: po rang gzugs tsam zhes gsungs pas sngar rdo rje
NK101(de)006:971: mdun nas khru bdun gyi sar dbu chen gyi h'u
NK101(de)006:972: sngon po rang gzugs tsam zhig gsal btab la sems
NK101(de)006:973: bzung / la lar rdo rje sngon po'i lte bar
NK101(de)006:974: h'u yig sgom tshul 'dug kyang gong gi rdo rje
NK101(de)006:975: dang 'khrul ba yin pas h'u kho na bsgoms pas
NK101(de)006:976: bzung / 'thus shing / sdod na h'u rig mnyam
NK101(de)006:977: par bzhag ces 'byung bas h'u yig sngon po de
NK101(de)006:978: la rig pa bstad de ci gnas su bzhag /'phro
NK101(de)006:979: na sa rdo ri brag dang ri rab gling bzhi
NK101(de)006:980: gling phran dang dgra gnyen khang khyim rang gi lus
NK101(de)006:981: yid 'ong grogs dang mdzes pa'i nor gang la 'phro
NK101(de)006:982: ba'i snang yul la chu srin dung gis phug pa
NK101(de)006:983: ltar phar thal tshur thal dag tu phug bdag med
NK101(de)006:984: bral nor lta bur bsams zhes gsungs pas shes pa
NK101(de)006:985: gang la 'phro ba'i snang yul sa rdo ri brag
NK101(de)006:986: ri rab gling bzhi gling phran sogs dang /
NK101(de)006:987: tshogs drug gi snang bar dgra gnyen khang khyim yid
NK101(de)006:988: du 'ong ba'i grogs dang nor rdzas sogs gang shar
NK101(de)006:989: ba la / h'u de las h'u yig grangs med pa spros te /
NK101(de)006:990: rgya mtshor bgrod pa'i tshong pa la chu srin ri
NK101(de)006:991: bo tsam rgyang ring po nas mthong ba ri dang
NK101(de)006:992: chu srin gang yin brtag phyir phug ron dang de
NK101(de)006:993: gsod pa'i phyir srog chags dung dkar gson ma btang
NK101(de)006:994: bas des chu srin gyi lus phug pas 'jigs pa
NK101(de)006:995: dang bral ba dper byas te /
NK101(de)006:996: h'u yig des snang yul de dag phar thal tshur
NK101(de)006:997: thal du khrol ma ltar phug pas 'dzin med du
NK101(de)006:998: btang zhing / mthar rang lus gdos bcas su snang
NK101(de)006:999: ba 'di yang spyi gtsug nas rkang mthil gyi bar
NK101(de)006:1000: du sha 'bus g.yengs pa ltar phug ste 'dzin med
NK101(de)006:1002: de ltar dmigs pa gsal thebs pa'i rtags ni /
NK101(de)006:1003: dmig sa pa gsal thebs rtags 'di 'byung yengs med
NK101(de)006:1004: rig pa lam du tshud rtog pa ci shar h'u
NK101(de)006:1005: du 'char dmigs pa gang la'ang bstad du 'dod ces
NK101(de)006:1006: gsungs pas 'phro gnas gang byung la gong bzhin gcun
NK101(de)006:1007: pas / ma yengs pa'i dran pa so tshugs shing /
NK101(de)006:1008: 'phro rgod thams cad h'u yig tu 'char ba dang dmigs pa gar bstad bde ba 'byung ngo //
NK101(de)006:1009: dmigs rkang 'di yang zhag grangs gong ma bzhin thun du bcad de sgom pa dang /
NK101(de)006:1010: de nas zhag gcig dal bar bya zhes pa yang gong ltar ro //
NK101(de)006:1011: gsum pa thig le dkar dmar la sems 'dzin pa ni /
NK101(de)006:1013: lus gnad rlung gnad rtsa gnad thig le'i gnad /
NK101(de)006:1014: bzhi la rten nas sems kyi gnas cha btsal /
NK101(de)006:1016: gong gi thig le dkar dmar dmigs rim skyong /
NK101(de)006:1017: zhes pa la sbyor rgyu yin pas thig le dkar dmar gyi sems 'dzin dang /
NK101(de)006:1018: gnad bzhi tha dad du yod pa ni ma yin te /
NK101(de)006:1020: pad+ma 'byung gnas thugs kyi bcud len pa lus kyi
NK101(de)006:1021: gnad ni mnyam gzhag drang por bsrang rtsa yi gnad
NK101(de)006:1022: ni mig gnyis thad kar blta rlung gi gnad ni
NK101(de)006:1023: steng rlung 'og rlung gcun shes pa'i gnad ni ma
NK101(de)006:1024: bcos lhug par bzhag ces dang /
NK101(de)006:1025: ka dag gi khrid gzhung las /
NK101(de)006:1026: lus gnad rkang pa skyil krung la lag pa mnyam
NK101(de)006:1027: gzhag rgal tshigs bsrang rtsa gnad mig gnyis rang por
NK101(de)006:1028: blta rlung gnad steng rlung 'og rlung bsdam thig le'i
NK101(de)006:1029: gnad la lte ba'i dbus e las thig le dmar
NK101(de)006:1030: po bsam spyi gtsug bde chen 'khor lo ru bam
NK101(de)006:1031: las thig le dkar po bsam shes pa'i gnad ni
NK101(de)006:1032: sum mdo ru e las me 'bar bam zhu nas
NK101(de)006:1033: snying gar thig le dkar dmar 'dres de la shes
NK101(de)006:1034: pa bstad de gzung yang dag don gyi gnad bstan
NK101(de)006:1035: pa thig le dkar dmar rim gyis bsdu ci yang
NK101(de)006:1036: yid la mi bya'o zhes gsungs pa'i phyir dmigs pa
NK101(de)006:1037: de gnyis gong 'og sbyar te nyams su len pa'i
NK101(de)006:1038: tshul ni / lus gnad rkang pa rdo rje skyil krung sogs rnam snang chos bdun spyi ltar la /
NK101(de)006:1040: bla ma'i gsung rgyun lag gnyis kyi mthe bong gis
NK101(de)006:1041: srin lag gi rtsa ba mnan te rdo rje bsdams
NK101(de)006:1042: pa barla gnyis kyi steng du bzhag ste /
NK101(de)006:1043: rlung ro dgu phrugs sam lan gsum bsal /
NK101(de)006:1044: lus kyi drang thad du rtsa dbu ma mtshan nyid bzhi ldan yar rtse tshangs bug dang /
NK101(de)006:1045: mar sna lte 'og sor bzhir zug pa las ro rkyang gnyis bsgom mi dgos /
NK101(de)006:1046: rtsa gnad mig gnyis rang babs su blta /
NK101(de)006:1047: lung gnad 'og rlung bskum zhing steng rlung sna bug nas barngubasa te lte 'og tu chir gyis mnan /
NK101(de)006:1048: thig le'i gnad lte ba'i thad kyi dbu ma'i nang
NK101(de)006:1049: du shes rab kyi rang bzhin e yig las byung
NK101(de)006:1050: ba'i thig le dmar po dbu ma sbom phra sba
NK101(de)006:1051: lcag tsam la thig le rgya sran tsam mda' smug
NK101(de)006:1052: tsam la sran ma tsam zhig gsal btab /
NK101(de)006:1053: spyi gtsug gi dbu ma'i nang du thabs kyi rang
NK101(de)006:1054: bzhin bam yig las byung ba'i thig le dkar po
NK101(de)006:1055: che chung gong dang 'dra ba gsal btab /
NK101(de)006:1056: shes pa'i gnad ni sum mdor a thung shad kyi
NK101(de)006:1057: rnam pa me'i rang bzhin can 'di lta bu zhig
NK101(de)006:1058: gsal btab / 'og rlung bskum pa'i rkyen gyis a shad la bus te mer 'bar ba /
NK101(de)006:1059: thig le dmar po dang 'dres te gyen du 'bar bas snying thad kyi dbu mar sleb /
NK101(de)006:1060: de las kyang me lce gyen du 'bar bas spyi
NK101(de)006:1061: bo'i thig le dkar po dngul chu ltar zhu ste
NK101(de)006:1062: snying ga'i thig le dmar po dang 'dres pa la
NK101(de)006:1063: sems bzung ste ci gnas su bzhag ste rlung bzung
NK101(de)006:1064: / mi thub pa dang sangs kyis btang ba sogs dang /
NK101(de)006:1065: yang gong bzhin gsal btab ste rlung 'dzin pa sogs thun rer ci nus bya /
NK101(de)006:1066: thun bsdu na mthar thig le dkar dmar gnyis kyang
NK101(de)006:1067: mi dmigs par bsam la ci yang yid la mi
NK101(de)006:1068: bya bar gang shar rang grol du mnyam par 'jog
NK101(de)006:1070: bar bar ngo bo bltas te shar grol btang ngo //
NK101(de)006:1072: de ltar gsal thebs pa'i rtags ni /
NK101(de)006:1073: dmigs pa gsal thebs rtags 'di 'byung lus kyi snang
NK101(de)006:1074: ba dran tshor med dbugs ni phyi nang 'gyu mi
NK101(de)006:1075: tshor snang ba thogs med 'gro bar shes zhes gsungs
NK101(de)006:1076: phan yon ni / de ltar dmigs pa gsum bsgoms
NK101(de)006:1077: pas lus ngag yid gsum lam du tshud ces gsungs
NK101(de)006:1078: phan yon ni / pas / rdo rje dkar pos lus /
NK101(de)006:1079: h'u sngon pos ngag thig le dkar dmar gyi sems gsum lam du tshud par 'gyur //
NK101(de)006:1080: dmigs pa de gsum sgom pa'i tshad ni /
NK101(de)006:1081: gang zag dbang po rim pa gsum dmigs pa re
NK101(de)006:1082: re bsgom pa'i tshad bdun dang bcu bzhi nyer gcig
NK101(de)006:1083: gis rang rang rtags re 'byung bar nges zhes gsungs
NK101(de)006:1084: pas / sngon 'gro gzer lnga nas 'di'i bar gyi dmigs rim rnams /
NK101(de)006:1087: tha mas nyer gcig re bsgoms na rtags de rnams
NK101(de)006:1088: 'byung nges pas zhag re tsam yang bsgom mi nus
NK101(de)006:1089: par nyams rtags 'byung dka' bas nyams khrid du byed
NK101(de)006:1090: na gzhung bzhin bya ba gces so //
NK101(de)006:1091: de ltar thun mong dang thun mong ma yin pa'i sngon 'gro rnams song rjes /
NK101(de)006:1092: dngos gzhi'i khrid kyi rim pa sems chos nyid kyi dkyil 'khor ni /
NK101(de)006:1094: de rjes khrid gzhung dngos gzhi la zhugs te /
NK101(de)006:1095: mnyam gzhag gsal stong 'dzin med ngo bo skyong /
NK101(de)006:1096: zhes gsungs pa'i don spyir zhi gnas sngon du btang
NK101(de)006:1097: ba'i mthar sems 'tshol gyis bdar sha bcad de bsgom
NK101(de)006:1098: thog nas lta ba 'tshol ba dang /
NK101(de)006:1099: thog mar sems 'tshol dang de nas zhi gnas su
NK101(de)006:1100: phab te blta thog nas bsgom 'tshol ba ste lugs
NK101(de)006:1101: gnyis las / 'dir snga ma ltar yin pas /
NK101(de)006:1102: dang po bsgom thog nas lta ba 'tshol ba ni /
NK101(de)006:1103: gong gi sems 'dzin de rnams la rim par slob pa dang /
NK101(de)006:1104: bla ma'i phyag bzhes su skabs 'dir rten can rde'u
NK101(de)006:1105: shing bu sogs la brten nas sems 'dzin pa dang
NK101(de)006:1106: / rten med ma bcos par 'jog pa sogs thabs
NK101(de)006:1107: sna tshogs kyi sgo nas zhi gnas bsgom gyi gzhi
NK101(de)006:1108: yin pas mnyam par 'jog dgos shing /
NK101(de)006:1109: de yang rnam rtog bkag bsgom lta bu ma yin par gzhi rtsa gcod pa'i phyir yin te /
NK101(de)006:1110: ka dag gi khrid gzhung las /
NK101(de)006:1111: de nas dben pa'i gnas chen du lus ngag yid
NK101(de)006:1112: gsum brtag par bya dus de yan chad dug lnga'i
NK101(de)006:1113: las ci byas ci dran bag chags yin me tog
NK101(de)006:1114: sad kyis khyer ba 'dra rjes 'breng mi bya 'brel
NK101(de)006:1115: thag bcad dus de man chad dug lnga'i las ci
NK101(de)006:1116: byas ci bsams nyon mongs yin sna thag dgra la
NK101(de)006:1117: shor ba 'dra bsam mno mi btang ci dgar bzhag
NK101(de)006:1118: da ltar shes pa dngas ma phyed thom me mun
NK101(de)006:1119: ne gti mug yin the tshom re dwogs rnam rtog
NK101(de)006:1120: yin rtog pa'i spun langs lta ba'i dgra ma bcos
NK101(de)006:1121: ma bcos rang so la ci yang yid la mi
NK101(de)006:1122: bya bar snang ba stong par rtogs pa dang stong
NK101(de)006:1123: pa snang bar rtogs pa dang snang stong dbyer med
NK101(de)006:1124: rtogs pa dang sangs rgyas sems can dbyer med du
NK101(de)006:1125: ma rtogs bar la dben pa bsten dbang po rab
NK101(de)006:1126: 'bring tha ma yis bdun gsum nyer gcig bsgoms pa
NK101(de)006:1127: yis nyams bzhi 'char bas nan tan bskyed ces dang
NK101(de)006:1128: / gu ru pad+ma dge slong nam mkha' snying por gsol 'debs su rtsal ba las /
NK101(de)006:1129: 'di ltar yid kyi yul du 'gyu ba yi nyon
NK101(de)006:1130: mongs dug lnga'i rtog pa ci shar yang sngon bsu
NK101(de)006:1131: rjes gcod blo yis bcos mi gzhug 'gyu ba rang
NK101(de)006:1132: sar bzhag pas chos skur grol ces gsungs pa ltar
NK101(de)006:1133: bsgom dgos pas / de yang gang zag gi rigs
NK101(de)006:1134: thod rgal rim skyes gcig car gsum gyi rgyud tshod
NK101(de)006:1135: dang sbyar ba'i khrid tshul bya dgos pas rten can
NK101(de)006:1136: rde'u shing bu sogs la brten kyang 'gal ba med
NK101(de)006:1137: bsgom dgos pas / mod / 'on kyang gong gi
NK101(de)006:1138: sems 'dzin rnams dmigs pa'i rten can kho na yin
NK101(de)006:1139: pas rde'u shing bu sogs kyi spros pa med kyang
NK101(de)006:1140: bsgom dgos pas / mod / chog cing / rten med kho na gzhung dang mthun pas /
NK101(de)006:1141: rnam snang chos bdun bcas te shes pa khong glod
NK101(de)006:1142: de mnyam par bzhag pas las dang pos tshogs drug
NK101(de)006:1143: gi rtog pa shugs che bas /
NK101(de)006:1144: phyi rol gyi rkyen las sems kyi rnam rtog dug
NK101(de)006:1145: lnga'i bag chags ldang gis shar ba de'i rjes mi
NK101(de)006:1146: gcod cing / ma 'ongs pa'i rtog pa'i sngon mi
NK101(de)006:1147: bsu da lta'i shes pa dngas snyigs ma phyed pa
NK101(de)006:1148: chu bo rnyog mas dkrugs pa lta bu mun thom
NK101(de)006:1149: du yod pa de dran shes kyi rig pas ngos
NK101(de)006:1151: rnam rtog thol skyes rbad gcod kyi tshul du gang
NK101(de)006:1152: shar gyi ngo bo rang shar rang grol du btang
NK101(de)006:1153: / las dang po par rnam rtog ri gzar la
NK101(de)006:1154: chu rgyug pa ltar 'byung yang skyon du mi blta
NK101(de)006:1155: bar ngos zin par byas pas /
NK101(de)006:1156: re zhig nas 'gyu ba je phrar 'gyur zhing gnas cha cher song ba'i dus /
NK101(de)006:1157: 'gyu ba phra mo rtsad ma chod pa'i gnas yod
NK101(de)006:1158: snyam pa'i bzang rtog a 'thas na zhi gnas ltem
NK101(de)006:1159: po'i 'gog pa'i snyoms 'jug lta bur 'gro bas 'gyu
NK101(de)006:1160: ba phra rags sbom gsum ngos gzung ste shar grol
NK101(de)006:1163: mkhar chen gza' la gsungs pa ka dag gi chos can zab mo gnad kyi thems bcu las /
NK101(de)006:1164: sems 'dzin gyi phur pa la zhen pas thar pa
NK101(de)006:1165: mi thob zhi gnas mgo byil gyis thar pa'i lam
NK101(de)006:1166: mi rnyed ces gsungs pa'i phyir /
NK101(de)006:1167: de ltar bsgoms pas nyams bzhi 'char tshul ni /
NK101(de)006:1168: ka dag gi ngo sprod rang rig rang gsal las /
NK101(de)006:1169: snang ba 'di stong par rtogs stong pa snang bar
NK101(de)006:1170: rtogs snang stong dbyer med du rtogs sangs rgyas dang
NK101(de)006:1171: sems can dbyer med du rtogs de nyid kyi gdengs
NK101(de)006:1172: rnyed pa'i shes pa 'byung zhes gsungs /
NK101(de)006:1173: de ltar shar yang chog shes dang 'dzin chags med pa zhig dgos te /
NK101(de)006:1175: nyams kyi snang ba bzhi la chog shes su gzung
NK101(de)006:1176: ba ni byis pa'i lta ba yin no snang ba
NK101(de)006:1177: dang stong pa 'di la ma chags pa zhig dgos
NK101(de)006:1179: snang ba dang stong pa dbyer med du 'dug snyam na /
NK101(de)006:1180: snang ba 'di la ma chags pa zhig dgos te zhes shog ser tsha la gdugs pa brtag go //
NK101(de)006:1181: de ltar bsgoms pa la gegs sel ba ni /
NK101(de)006:1183: phyi gegs sel byed gu ru spyi bor bsgom /
NK101(de)006:1184: tho rengs dus su h'u gi snang glu blangs /
NK101(de)006:1185: bla ma'i thugs dang rang gi shes pa bsre /
NK101(de)006:1186: zhes gsungs pa spyir phyi'i gegs sel thabs su /
NK101(de)006:1187: lus mnyam gzhag gi mig nam mkhar bstad /
NK101(de)006:1188: shes pa ma bcos pa'i ngang nas rang gi spyi
NK101(de)006:1189: bor bla ma rdo rje drag po rtsal gyi sku'i
NK101(de)006:1191: gsol 'debs kyi tshul du gdung shugs drag pos rgyas
NK101(de)006:1192: pa'i h'u bdun brtsegs kyi snang glu blangs pas mos
NK101(de)006:1193: gus kyi nyams skyes pa dang /
NK101(de)006:1194: de nyid 'od phung sngon po'i rnam par zhu ste
NK101(de)006:1195: rang la thim pas bla ma dang rang sems dbyer
NK101(de)006:1196: med du mnyam par bzhag go /'di ni khrid gzhung
NK101(de)006:1197: dngos gzhi las / pad+ma 'byung gnas thugs kyi bcud
NK101(de)006:1198: len pa lus kyi gnad ni mnyam gzhag drang por
NK101(de)006:1199: bsrang rtsa yi gnad ni mig gnyis thad kar bstad
NK101(de)006:1200: dngos gzhi las / / rlung gi gnad ni steng
NK101(de)006:1201: rlung 'og rlung gcun shes pa'i gnad ni ma bcos
NK101(de)006:1202: lhug par bazhagah tho rangs dus na h'u gi snang
NK101(de)006:1203: glu blangs bla ma spyi bor bsgom zhing gsol ba
NK101(de)006:1204: gdab ma bcos rtse gcig gdung ba skyes pa'i tshe
NK101(de)006:1205: bla ma'i thugs dang rang gi shes pa bsre mnyam
NK101(de)006:1206: gzhag ngag la rig pa dar cig bzhag ces gsungs
NK101(de)006:1207: dngos gzhi las / / pa'i don no // bye
NK101(de)006:1208: brag tu sgom skyon lnga sel ba'i dang po bying
NK101(de)006:1209: ba gti mug gi gegs sel ni /
NK101(de)006:1211: de nas nang gi sgom skyon lnga sel phyir /
NK101(de)006:1212: bying ba gti mug 'thibs pa'i gegs byung na /
NK101(de)006:1213: gu ru dmar smug nam mkha'i mthongs su bsgom /
NK101(de)006:1214: 'od zhu rang la thim sogs gzhung bzhin bskyang /
NK101(de)006:1215: zhes pa'i don khrid gzhung las /
NK101(de)006:1216: de la bsgom gyi skyon lnga bsal ba ni bying
NK101(de)006:1217: zhing 'thibs na gti mug las ngan slong lus dang
NK101(de)006:1218: shes pa gzengs bstod shes pa bsgrims mtho sa rlung
NK101(de)006:1219: gi gser bu 'ong sa ru lus gnad bcos te
NK101(de)006:1220: shes pa nam mkhar bstad gu ru dmar smug mdangs
NK101(de)006:1221: ldan bdag la bstim rjes la mnyam gzhag ma bcos
NK101(de)006:1222: ngang la bzhag zhag gsum 'bad na gti mug mun
NK101(de)006:1223: pa sel zhes pa'i sgom don bying rmugs kyi ngang
NK101(de)006:1224: du song na bying ba gti mug gi gegs yin
NK101(de)006:1225: pas / de sel ba ni sa mtho sa rlung bser bu yod par lus gnad gong bzhin bya /
NK101(de)006:1226: shes pa gzengs bstod de bsgrims la nam mkhar bstad /
NK101(de)006:1227: bla ma gu ru drag po rtsal gyi sku'am gu
NK101(de)006:1228: ru zhi ba gang yang rung ba sku mdog dmar
NK101(de)006:1229: smug tu yod pa mdangs dang ldan pa zhig mdun
NK101(de)006:1230: gyi nam mkhar bsgoms pa de la shes pa bstad
NK101(de)006:1231: cing gdung shugs kyi gsol 'debs yid kyis byas pa'i
NK101(de)006:1232: mthar de nyid 'od zer dmar smug gcig tu gyur
NK101(de)006:1233: nas rang la bstim nas mnyam par 'jog pa zhag
NK101(de)006:1234: gsum bsgom mo // gnyis pa rgod pa zhe sdang gi gegs sel ba ni /
NK101(de)006:1236: rgod pa zhe sdang gegs sel gu ru dkar /
NK101(de)006:1237: smin mtshams thad kyi nam mkhar bsgom pa dang /
NK101(de)006:1240: rnam rtog hrags shing rgod na zhe sdang slong nga
NK101(de)006:1241: yi sku la blta stangs rig pa bstad rang 'dra'i
NK101(de)006:1242: lha skus 'jig rten thams cad gang dpa' zhing ngar
NK101(de)006:1243: ldan sku che yan lag hrags drag po'i h'u sgra
NK101(de)006:1244: ngar ldan dir ri ri dgra gnyen rtsis gdab med
NK101(de)006:1245: par shes pa bsgrim gu ru dkar gsal rang gi
NK101(de)006:1246: thugs kar thim / shes pa glod kyin mnyam gzhag
NK101(de)006:1247: ngang la bzhag zhag gsum bsgoms na zhe sdang rtog
NK101(de)006:1249: rnam rtog 'phro rgod che ba zhe sdang gi rtog
NK101(de)006:1250: pa 'phel ba'i gegs yin pas de sel ba ni
NK101(de)006:1251: / mdun gyi smin mtshams thad kyi nam mkhar gu
NK101(de)006:1252: ru zhi drag gang rigs kyi sku dkar gsal zhig
NK101(de)006:1253: gsal btab pa la rig pa bstad cing lta stangs
NK101(de)006:1254: byas te yid kyis gsol ba btab pas mthar 'od
NK101(de)006:1255: zer dkar po'i rnam par gyur nas rang la bstim
NK101(de)006:1257: skabs 'gar mdun gyi gu ru'i sku dang /
NK101(de)006:1258: rang yang snang ba ma 'gags rig pa lha sku
NK101(de)006:1259: rdo rje drag po rtsal gyi skur shar ba las
NK101(de)006:1260: / gu ru drag po'i sku dpa' zhing ngar dang
NK101(de)006:1261: ldan pa sku che la yan lag rags pa zhal
NK101(de)006:1262: nas drag po'i h'u sgra 'brug sgra ltar dir ri
NK101(de)006:1263: ri sgrog pa dpag tu med pa 'phros nas 'jig
NK101(de)006:1264: rten gyi khams thams cad gang ste dgra gnyen gyi
NK101(de)006:1265: snang ba gang shar yang rtsis gdab med par bcoms
NK101(de)006:1266: pa la shes pa bsgrims te bstad pa'i mthar lhod
NK101(de)006:1267: kyis glod la mnyam par 'jog pa zhag gsum bsgom
NK101(de)006:1268: / mo // gsum pa za zi'i rtog pa sna
NK101(de)006:1269: tshogs su 'phro zhing mnyam gzhag la mi gnas par
NK101(de)006:1270: phyi rol gyi yul snang rgod pa'i gegs sel ni
NK101(de)006:1272: 'phro dang shes pa rdzi 'khor gegs byung na /
NK101(de)006:1273: lte ba'i gnas nas me 'bar snod bcud dang /
NK101(de)006:1274: phung khams bsregs nas stong nyid ngang la 'jog /'phro na gu ru mthing ga snying thad bsgom /
NK101(de)006:1275: de yang 'od zhu rang la thim par bsam /
NK101(de)006:1277: shes pa s+dzi 'khor za zi rtog pa mang mnyam
NK101(de)006:1278: gzhag mi brtan yul snang rgod pa na lte ba'i
NK101(de)006:1279: 'og nas me byung rang lus bsregs me dpung phyir
NK101(de)006:1280: 'phel phyi yi yul mkhar dang dgra gnyen mdzes sdug
NK101(de)006:1281: 'dzin pa'i yul snang bsregs thams cad stong pa chen
NK101(de)006:1282: po'i ngang la bzhag gu ru mthing ga bdag gi
NK101(de)006:1283: thugs kar bstim 'dzin med ngang la zhag gsum mnyam
NK101(de)006:1284: par bzhag des ni rnam rtog rkun po lam du
NK101(de)006:1286: de lta bu'i gegs sel ba ni /
NK101(de)006:1287: rang gi lte 'og na gzhir gnas kyi me a
NK101(de)006:1288: thung shad kyi rnam par yod pa de las me
NK101(de)006:1289: 'bar te rang lus gdos bcas su snang ba 'adiyanga
NK101(de)006:1291: de las me dpung cher 'phel nas snod kyi 'jig
NK101(de)006:1292: rten sa rdo ri brag yul mkhar sogs dang bcud
NK101(de)006:1293: kyi sems can dgra gnyen mdzes sdug 'dzin pa'i yul
NK101(de)006:1294: snang thams cad bsregs te thams cad stong pa chen
NK101(de)006:1295: po'i ngang du mnyam par bzhag /
NK101(de)006:1296: gu ru drag po mthing ga zhig nam mkhar bsgoms
NK101(de)006:1297: pa la yid kyis gsol ba btab pas 'od zer
NK101(de)006:1298: mthing ga'i rnam par gyur te rang gi snying gar
NK101(de)006:1299: thim par bsams la 'dzin med kyi ngang du 'jog
NK101(de)006:1300: pa zhag gsum byas pas rnam rtog rkun po zhes
NK101(de)006:1301: 'gyu ba phra rags rtsad mi chod pa'i 'og 'gyu
NK101(de)006:1302: rgya 'byams kyi gegs las grol bar 'gyur ro //
NK101(de)006:1303: bzhi pa shes pa s+dzi 'khor ba dang re dwogs bdag 'dzin gyi gegs sel ni /
NK101(de)006:1305: skabs 'gar bde sdug re dwogs sna tshogs pa'i /
NK101(de)006:1306: snang ba gang shar chu yi ri mo'am /
NK101(de)006:1307: sbrul mdud bzhin du rang grol ngang du btang //
NK101(de)006:1308: de la mi gnas gu ru 'od lnga yin /
NK101(de)006:1309: rnam par sems bstad 'od zhu rang la thim /
NK101(de)006:1310: 'dzin med ngang la zhag gcig mnyam par bzhag /
NK101(de)006:1312: gtad med bsgoms kyang shes pa s+dzi 'khor nas re
