NK101(de)006:1313: dwogs bdag 'dzin dam pos 'thas pa na snang sems
NK101(de)006:1314: bya byed thams cad 'khrul pa yin skye 'chi 'pho
NK101(de)006:1315: 'gyur mi rtag dran par gyis 'jigs skrag tsha grang
NK101(de)006:1316: nad kyang sgyu ma yin bskal par dmyal bar phyin
NK101(de)006:1317: nas btsos bsregs kyang sems la skye 'chi med pas
NK101(de)006:1318: 'thon pa yin zas nor nye 'brel snying brtse sgyu
NK101(de)006:1319: ma yin rang lus gces par gzung yang nam zhig
NK101(de)006:1320: 'chi 'khor ba'i sgyu ni re dwogs the tshom yin
NK101(de)006:1321: sangs rgyas dgongs pa stong gsal 'dzin med yin dper
NK101(de)006:1322: na nam mkha' sprin dang bral ba de gsal dngas
NK101(de)006:1323: bkrag 'tsher ngos gzung gcig kyang med de phyir skyes
NK101(de)006:1325: nam mkha' man shel dag la shes pa bstad rig
NK101(de)006:1326: pa ngar ldan phyogs zhen 'dzin chags dor bcos med
NK101(de)006:1327: ngang la mnyam gzhag dar cig bzhag gu ru 'od
NK101(de)006:1328: zer lnga ldan bdag la bstim de ltar zhag gsum
NK101(de)006:1329: bsgoms pas the tshom chod ces gsungs pas de'i don
NK101(de)006:1331: bde sdug re dwogs kyi snang ba gang shar chu'i
NK101(de)006:1332: ri mo'am sbrul gyi mdud pa bzhin du rang grol
NK101(de)006:1333: ba / gnas lugs gtad med rang babs su mnyam
NK101(de)006:1334: par bzhag kyang shes pa s+dzi 'khor nas re dwogs
NK101(de)006:1335: dang bdag 'dzin gyi mdud pa ma 'khrol na 'di
NK101(de)006:1336: ba / ltar bsams te / phyi snang ba la
NK101(de)006:1337: sems g.yengs pa'i bya byed kyi blo sna tshogs su
NK101(de)006:1338: shar na thams cad 'khrul par ngo shes par byas
NK101(de)006:1339: te skye 'chi dang 'pho 'gyur thams cad mi rtag
NK101(de)006:1341: 'dir snang gi sems la 'jigs skrag dang lus la
NK101(de)006:1342: tsha grang dang nad sogs thams cad rtag pa ma
NK101(de)006:1343: yin par sgyu mar shes pa dang /
NK101(de)006:1344: sgyu mtshan sems snang gi 'khrul ngor dmyal bar bskal
NK101(de)006:1345: pa du mar btso sreg gi sdug bsngal myong yang
NK101(de)006:1346: sems la skye 'chi med pa'i phyir dmyal ba nas
NK101(de)006:1347: 'thon pa dang / tshe 'dir zas nor nye 'brel
NK101(de)006:1348: la snying brtse zhing chags kyang sgyu ma yin phyir
NK101(de)006:1351: nye 'brel zas nor ri kha'i r+ts+wa sbur 'dra ji
NK101(de)006:1352: ltar byas kyang 'bral bas brtse sems dor zhes gsungs
NK101(de)006:1353: / rang gi lus 'di gces par gzung yang nam
NK101(de)006:1354: zhig 'chi bar 'gyur bas de'i phyir 'khor bar 'khyams
NK101(de)006:1355: pa'i sgyu bzang por re ba dang ngan par dwogs
NK101(de)006:1356: pa'i the tshom gyi blos 'ching ba yin pas 'dzin
NK101(de)006:1357: med sgyu mar shes pa dang /
NK101(de)006:1358: mthar thug sangs rgyas kyi dgongs pa yang stong gsal
NK101(de)006:1359: 'dzin med nam mkha' sprin bral ltar ngos gzung med
NK101(de)006:1360: pa'i phyir rang gi shes pa s+dzi 'khor ba las
NK101(de)006:1361: hur gyis bton / phyi rol gyi nam mkha' dang
NK101(de)006:1362: man shel g.ya' bral la rig pa bstad la dbyings
NK101(de)006:1363: rig bsres te 'dzin med ma bcos pa'i ngang du
NK101(de)006:1364: mnyam par bzhag /'di la rtsa bar zhag gcig mnyam
NK101(de)006:1365: par 'jog tshul bshad kyang khrid gzhung du dar cig
NK101(de)006:1366: hur gyis bton / bzhag / ces gsungs pas rjes
NK101(de)006:1367: thob kyi snang ba la shar bar du dar cig
NK101(de)006:1368: mnyam par 'jog pa'i don yin par rtogs /
NK101(de)006:1369: mnyam gzhag de la ma gnas par rtog pa'i spun langs na /
NK101(de)006:1370: gu ru zhi drag gi sku 'char gang bde 'od
NK101(de)006:1371: zer lnga 'phro ba zhig mdun gyi nam mkhar gsal
NK101(de)006:1372: btab pa la sems bzung ste yid kyis gsol ba
NK101(de)006:1373: btab mthar rang la bstim nas mnyam par 'jog pa
NK101(de)006:1374: zhag gsum sgom par gsungs pa ltar bya /
NK101(de)006:1375: lnga pa zhi gnas kyi gzhi bca' ba dang /
NK101(de)006:1376: de la dug gsum bye brag gi gegs sel ba yin pa rtsa bar /
NK101(de)006:1377: de nas lus sems snang sems brtag par bya /
NK101(de)006:1378: zhes sogs bshad pa 'og tu sems 'tshol gyi skabs su 'chad cing /
NK101(de)006:1379: 'dir khrid gzhung gi sa bcad mi stongs pa'i phyir lnga pa'i don mdo tsam brjod na /
NK101(de)006:1381: snang ba rang snang grag pa rang sgra yin 'gyu
NK101(de)006:1382: ba rang stong yin pas ngang la zhog de ltar
NK101(de)006:1383: bsgoms pas rnam rtog je nyung 'gro gsal stong rig
NK101(de)006:1384: pa'i gdangs ni je ring 'phel dran thag ji nye
NK101(de)006:1385: rtog pa nyal gyis zhi lus kyi snang ba dran
NK101(de)006:1386: tshor med pa la srog rtsol rlung gi 'byung 'jug
NK101(de)006:1387: mi tshor zhing shes pa g.yo med rgya mtsho rlabs
NK101(de)006:1388: bral 'dra de ni bsgom gyi gzhi yin med thabs
NK101(de)006:1389: med zhi gnas zhes bya bsgom gyi zhing sa yin
NK101(de)006:1390: zhes gsungs pas phyii rol snang grags kyi yul la
NK101(de)006:1391: 'gyu byed kyi dran pa rang gi ngo bos stong
NK101(de)006:1393: rnam rtog 'phro rgod je nyung du song yang dran
NK101(de)006:1394: shes kyi gsal cha ma 'gags pa'i ngo bo stong
NK101(de)006:1395: pa rig gdangs rang ngo rang shes kyi dran pa
NK101(de)006:1396: rtsol med du nye bar 'char bas 'phro rgod kyi
NK101(de)006:1397: 'gyu ba nyal gyis zhi ba lus snang dran tshor
NK101(de)006:1398: med pa rlung 'byung rngub mi tshor ba shes pa
NK101(de)006:1399: rgya mtsho rlabs bral ltar mi g.yo bar gnas pa
NK101(de)006:1400: de zhi gnas yin pas de bsgom gyi gzhi bca'
NK101(de)006:1401: ba zhing sa lta bu yin pa'i don /
NK101(de)006:1402: de ltar zhi gnas kyi ro la chags pa'i zhen
NK101(de)006:1403: pa spang thabs rnams khrid gzhung gi tshigs bcad gong
NK101(de)006:1404: 'og 'khrugs sdebs kyi don bsdus te bshad na /
NK101(de)006:1405: sngar ma phyin pa'i dben gnas shig tu phyin pas
NK101(de)006:1406: rtog pa gsar pa zhig lhang gi 'char bar 'gyur
NK101(de)006:1407: bas de rig pas bkug ste ngo bo la cher
NK101(de)006:1408: gyis bltas pas rnam rtog dang po byung sa dang
NK101(de)006:1409: / tha mar 'gro sa med pa da lta'i bar
NK101(de)006:1410: gyi shes pa 'tshub ril rang gis rang bcings pa'i
NK101(de)006:1411: 'khrul pa de lta bu lhod kyis glod de 'jog
NK101(de)006:1412: / / de bzhin du dur khrod dang khang stong /
NK101(de)006:1413: ngam 'brog g.yang sa dgra bgegs gnyen dang nor rdzas
NK101(de)006:1414: sogs chags sdang skye ba'i yul rnams su rim par
NK101(de)006:1415: bgrod pas rtog pa gsar pa re skye bas /
NK101(de)006:1417: de nas rim gyi dur khrod khang stong dang ngam
NK101(de)006:1418: 'brog g.yang sa dgra bgegs chags sdang yul rim par
NK101(de)006:1419: bgrod pas rtog pa gsar ba skye zhes gsungs pas
NK101(de)006:1420: dug gsum bye brag gi gegs sel las /
NK101(de)006:1421: zhe sdang gi gegs sel ni /
NK101(de)006:1422: de yang dgra bgegs lta bur zhe sdang dang 'jigs skrag skyes na /
NK101(de)006:1424: zhe sdang skyes na de yi ngo bo blta dgra
NK101(de)006:1425: bo gnyen du 'gyur srid sgyu ma yin zhes dang
NK101(de)006:1426: / dgra 'dre'i rkyen gyis 'jigs shing skrag pa na
NK101(de)006:1427: gces pa'i 'dzin pa dam pos byung ba ste lus
NK101(de)006:1428: 'di skrag na chu lbur sa rdo 'dra ji ltar
NK101(de)006:1429: byas kyang 'chi bas rgyangs kyis skyur zhes dang /
NK101(de)006:1430: dgra dang 'dre yang rmi lam snang ba 'dra gnyid
NK101(de)006:1431: kyi dgra 'dre sad dus gang na 'dug de bzhin
NK101(de)006:1432: da lta'i 'dzin snang 'dis 'phung bas 'dzin snang dor
NK101(de)006:1433: na sems la dgras mi 'jigs lhod glod rgyangs bskyur
NK101(de)006:1434: ma bcos ngang la zhog ces gsungs pas dgra la
NK101(de)006:1435: zhe sdang drag po skyes na de yi ngo bor
NK101(de)006:1436: bltas de mnyam par bzhag pas dgra 'dzin gyi snang
NK101(de)006:1437: ba rang sar zhig pas dgra yang mnyen du 'gyur
NK101(de)006:1439: dgra dang 'drer 'dzin gyi rnam rtog a 'thas pas
NK101(de)006:1440: 'jigs skrag gi snang ba shar na rang nyid gces
NK101(de)006:1441: 'dzin gyi 'jur bu dam po las byung bas 'di
NK101(de)006:1442: ltar bsams te lus 'di skrag na chu bur sa
NK101(de)006:1443: rdo dang 'dra bas gces par gzung yang nam zhig
NK101(de)006:1444: na 'chi la / dgra 'dre'i snang ba shar ba
NK101(de)006:1445: yang rmi lam dang 'dra bas gnyis sad pa'i tshe
NK101(de)006:1447: gnyis 'dzin gyi snang ba dor na rang sar grol
NK101(de)006:1448: bas lhod kyis glod la ma bcos par bzhag /'dod
NK101(de)006:1451: 'dod chags skyes na de yi ngo bo blta sha
NK101(de)006:1452: khrag lang 'tsho mi rtag rmi lam 'dra gang la'ang
NK101(de)006:1453: snying po med kyi chags zhen bskyungs 'dzin med dran
NK101(de)006:1454: pa mnyam gzhag brtan par mdzod ces gsungs pas 'dod
NK101(de)006:1455: chags skyes na de'i ngo bo la blta zhing chags
NK101(de)006:1456: yul gyi sha khrag lang tsho thams cad mi rtag
NK101(de)006:1457: cing rga bar 'gyur ba dang mi sdug pa'i rang
NK101(de)006:1458: bzhin rmi lam 'dra bas chags zhen gyi blo bskyur
NK101(de)006:1460: gti mug gi gegs sel ni /
NK101(de)006:1462: shes pa s+dzi 'khor gsal cha ma thon na dran
NK101(de)006:1463: pas rgyur gzung bdag la gsol ba thob ma rig
NK101(de)006:1464: bag chags 'thibs po dran pas gzung shes pa gzengs
NK101(de)006:1465: bstod mnyam gzhag dar cig mdzod ces gsungs pas bying
NK101(de)006:1466: zhing 'thibs te shes pa s+dzi 'khor nas gti mug
NK101(de)006:1467: gi dbang gis gsal cha ma thon na /
NK101(de)006:1468: dran 'dzin gyi ngang nas gu ru spyi bor bsgoms
NK101(de)006:1469: shing mos gus kyi gsol ba btab ste shes pa
NK101(de)006:1470: gzengs bstod cing mnyam bzhag bya /
NK101(de)006:1471: 'di ni gu ru pad+mas rig 'dzin rgod ldem can
NK101(de)006:1472: la dag snang du zhal gdams ngo sprod gsungs pa
NK101(de)006:1473: las / rkyen snang the tshom gyis sems kyi rgyud
NK101(de)006:1474: bkrugs nas ci yang byed ma shes par shes pa
NK101(de)006:1475: s+dzi 'khor na rig pa rang lugs kyi ngang nas
NK101(de)006:1476: bla ma la gsol ba thob /
NK101(de)006:1477: de'i rjes bu shar ba'i blo gros rnam rtog gis
NK101(de)006:1478: ma bslad pa de sgro 'dogs chod pa'i snying gtam
NK101(de)006:1479: yin no // zhes gsungs pa dang don gcig par snang /
NK101(de)006:1480: de ltar dug gsum gyis kun nas bskyed pa'i bag
NK101(de)006:1481: chags rnam rtog gi rang gzugs na ba dang 'chi
NK101(de)006:1482: ba'i rnam rtog gi sdug bsngal shar na de dag
NK101(de)006:1483: gi byung gnas 'gro gsum brtag pa dang lam du
NK101(de)006:1485: na dang 'chi ba'i sdug bsngal byung ba'i tshe de
NK101(de)006:1486: yi byung sa gnas sa ngo bo blta na ba
NK101(de)006:1487: gces 'dzin 'thas pa'i bag chags yin sdug bsngal shi
NK101(de)006:1488: yi dwogs pa'i rnam rtog yin zug gzer nyon mongs
NK101(de)006:1489: las kyi rnam smin yin legs par brtags na yang
NK101(de)006:1490: dag chos sku ste na ba'i dus na gar yang
NK101(de)006:1491: song ba med gces 'dzin mi bya 'chi ba'i 'jigs
NK101(de)006:1492: pa dor zug gzer ro la mi myang mnyam par
NK101(de)006:1493: bzhag de phyir skyon rnams ci byung thams cad la
NK101(de)006:1494: byung sa 'gro sa gnas sa legs par brtag don
NK101(de)006:1495: la rgyu rkyen med do 'dzin pa chod ma bcos
NK101(de)006:1496: ngang la mnyam gzhag brtan par bya de yis lam
NK101(de)006:1497: gyi gegs dang bar chod sel zhes gsungs pa'i don
NK101(de)006:1498: lus la nad byung ba'i tshe nad de dang po
NK101(de)006:1499: gang nas byung bar du gang du gnas tha mar
NK101(de)006:1500: gang du 'gro brtag cing nad kyi ngo bo la
NK101(de)006:1501: blta / de yang gces 'dzin 'thas pa'i bag chags las nad dang /
NK101(de)006:1502: de'i sdug bsngal shi dwogs kyi rnam rtog dang zug
NK101(de)006:1503: gzer sngon las kyi rnam smin du shes pas zug
NK101(de)006:1504: gzer gyi ro mi myang zhing legs par brtags na
NK101(de)006:1505: rnam rtog gi rang gzugs chos sku bde ba chen
NK101(de)006:1506: por 'char zhing de bzhin du rkyen bzang ngan thams
NK101(de)006:1507: cad kyi byung gnas 'gro gsum brtag cing mkhan po
NK101(de)006:1508: rtsad chod pas ma bcos pa'i ngang la mnyam par
NK101(de)006:1509: bzhag pas lam gyi gegs dang bar chod thams cad
NK101(de)006:1511: ka dag gi chos sde gegs sel nor bu'i bang mdzod las /
NK101(de)006:1512: de ltar sgo gsum rang lugs su bzhag pas rnam
NK101(de)006:1513: rtog phra rags thams cad zhi nas sems rang sar
NK101(de)006:1514: lhag ge gnas pa cig 'byung de ka la zhi
NK101(de)006:1515: gnas zhes bya'o zhes gsungs pa'i phyir ro //
NK101(de)006:1516: 'di yan chad sems 'dzin gyi zhi gnas su bzhag
NK101(de)006:1517: thabs de dag gi gegs sel dang bcas pa'i rim
NK101(de)006:1518: pa'o // gnyis pa blta thog nas bsgom 'tshol ba
NK101(de)006:1519: sems 'tshol gyi sgo nas bdar sha gcad pa ni
NK101(de)006:1521: de nas lus sems snang sems brtag par bya /
NK101(de)006:1522: byung gnas 'gro gsum brtags la phu thag bcad /
NK101(de)006:1523: ces gsungs pa khrid gzhung du lus sems dang snang sems brtag pa ma gsungs kyang /
NK101(de)006:1524: bla ma'i gsung rgyun lus las sems byung ngam sems
NK101(de)006:1525: las lus byung brtags pas nyams myong gang byung bla
NK101(de)006:1526: mar zhu / snang sems gnyis kyang de dang mtshungs par brtag /
NK101(de)006:1527: de dag gi don 'og tu ngo sprod kyi skabs su ston /
NK101(de)006:1528: byung gnas 'gro gsum rtag pa ni /
NK101(de)006:1530: de nas rnal 'byor sems kyi ngo bo blta dang
NK101(de)006:1531: po zhag gsum sems kyi byung sa bsam byung sa
NK101(de)006:1532: 'dug na de yi rtsa ba brtag byung sa med
NK101(de)006:1533: na rgyu med ci la srid de nas zhag gsum
NK101(de)006:1534: sems kyi kha dog dang gzugs dang dbyibs su grub
NK101(de)006:1535: bam ma grub blta grub na legs par de yi
NK101(de)006:1536: rtsa ba bcad ma grub 'dug na 'phro 'du ci
NK101(de)006:1537: las byung de nas zhag gsum sems kyi 'gro sa
NK101(de)006:1538: brtag 'gro sa 'dug na de yi rtsa ba bcad
NK101(de)006:1539: 'gro sa med na blo gtad ji ltar byed kha
NK101(de)006:1540: tsam tshig tsam ma yin legs par brtag ces gsungs
NK101(de)006:1541: pa'i don sems zhes bya ba 'di dang po gang
NK101(de)006:1542: nas byung / bar du gang du gnas /
NK101(de)006:1548: kha dog dkar dmar sogs ji 'drar snang //
NK101(de)006:1549: gcig dang du ma ji lta bu zhig /
NK101(de)006:1550: gcig tu 'dug na de yang ji lta bu /
NK101(de)006:1551: mang por 'dug na grangs ji tsam /
NK101(de)006:1552: phyi rol tshogs drug gi yul snang gang du gnas /
NK101(de)006:1553: rang lus kyi spyi bo nas rkang mthil gyi bar gang du gnas /
NK101(de)006:1554: mang por 'dug na so sor dbyibs kha dog sogs su grub pa gzhir bcas pas ji ltar snang /
NK101(de)006:1555: gcig por 'dug na de yang gzugs dbyibs sogs ci 'dra ba zhig /
NK101(de)006:1556: lus 'dir sems gnas pa'i phyir lus kyi nang nas phyir 'phro ba'i tshe /
NK101(de)006:1557: phyi rol tu 'phro ba'i sems dang /
NK101(de)006:1558: nang du gnas pa'i sems gnyis su byung bas gnyis su snang ngam /
NK101(de)006:1559: gcig tu 'dug na phyir 'phro ba'i tshe nang na
NK101(de)006:1560: sems med pa shi ba'i ro dang 'dra ba zhig
NK101(de)006:1561: 'dug gam ji ltar yin sogs khrid gzhung ltar na
NK101(de)006:1563: dbang rtul la der yang ma tshad pa'i zhag mang
NK101(de)006:1564: po'i bar rtog tu 'jug cing bla mas so sor
NK101(de)006:1565: dri ba len 'di skabs 'ga' zhig gis brtag dpyad
NK101(de)006:1566: ma btang bar 'ol tshod kyi lan 'debs pa dang
NK101(de)006:1567: / 'ga' zhig gis dpe la bltas pa'i lan 'debs
NK101(de)006:1568: pa sogs sna tshogs yong bas rig thog nas bdar
NK101(de)006:1569: sha bcad pa'i dris lan tshul bzhin ma byung gi
NK101(de)006:1570: bar du sprod la rings rgyu med pas yang yang
NK101(de)006:1571: bskyar zhing dri ba rdo rus thug par len pa
NK101(de)006:1572: / gnad du che'o // de ltar sems 'tshol gyi rim pa 'di yan chad sngon 'gro'i rim pa'o //
NK101(de)006:1573: dngos gzhi thog mar byung gnas 'gro gsum sogs ngo sprod pa'i rim pa la /
NK101(de)006:1575: de nas sems nyid stong gsal 'dzin med de /
NK101(de)006:1576: ye nas sku gsum yin par ngo sprad de /
NK101(de)006:1577: ngo bo stong pa chos sku de yi mdangs /
NK101(de)006:1578: rang bzhin gsal ba longs spyod rdzogs sku dang /
NK101(de)006:1579: thugs rje cir yang ma 'gags sprul sku ste /
NK101(de)006:1580: don la rang rig ma bcos rjen pa 'di /
NK101(de)006:1581: gsal stong dbyer med snang stong dbyer med dang /
NK101(de)006:1582: rig stong dbyer med gsal le sing nge ba /
NK101(de)006:1583: yer re spros pa'i mtha' dang bral ba 'di /
NK101(de)006:1584: ye nas sku gsum bla ma rang bcas yin /
NK101(de)006:1585: zhes gsungs pa'i don khrid gzhung las /
NK101(de)006:1586: nges par go na sems kyi ngo bo 'di dang
NK101(de)006:1587: po byung sa med de nam mkha' 'dra sa gzhi
NK101(de)006:1588: rang yang stong pa'i ngang las grub ngos gzung med
NK101(de)006:1589: pa ci yang skye ba ste sa gzhi lo tog
NK101(de)006:1590: sems can skye 'chi dang nam mkha'i sprin dang char
NK101(de)006:1591: dang 'brug bzhin no sems kyi gzugs dang kha dog
NK101(de)006:1592: dbyibs rnams ni ngos gzung med de stong pa'i rang
NK101(de)006:1593: gdangs yin sna tshogs cir yang 'char bas 'khrul pa'i
NK101(de)006:1594: lam tha ma sems kyi 'gro sa ga la srid
NK101(de)006:1595: dper na gling bzhi'i 'jig rten 'jig pa'i tshe stong
NK101(de)006:1596: pa chen po nam mkha'i ngang du thim nam mkha'
NK101(de)006:1597: stong pa dag la 'jig rgyu med de bzhin lus
NK101(de)006:1598: dang 'dzin pa'i yul snang zhig stong par 'gro ste
NK101(de)006:1599: sems 'di stongs pa med mdor na sems kyi ngo
NK101(de)006:1600: bo gsal stong yin de la zhen chags phyogs 'dzin
NK101(de)006:1601: byed pa 'khrul rig pa bcos med rang shar 'dzin
NK101(de)006:1602: med ltos zhes gsungs pa ltar 'chad pa ni /
NK101(de)006:1603: dang po sems kyi byung sa nam mkha' dang 'dra ba'i stong pa yin pas /
NK101(de)006:1604: dper na snod kyi 'jig rten sa gzhi sogs kyang
NK101(de)006:1605: stong pa'i ngang las grub pas ngos gzung med pa
NK101(de)006:1606: las ci yang skye ba ste sa gzhi lo tog
NK101(de)006:1607: sems can skye 'chi thams cad nam mkhar sprin dang
NK101(de)006:1608: de las char dang 'brug grag pa bzhin no //
NK101(de)006:1609: sems la gzugs dang kha dog dbyibs rnams ngos gzung
NK101(de)006:1610: med kyang stong pa'i rang mdangs tshogs drug gi yul
NK101(de)006:1611: snang so sor cir yang 'char bas 'khrul pa yin
NK101(de)006:1612: no // bar du sems kyi gnas pa gcig tu ma nges kyang /
NK101(de)006:1613: rang snang la shar ba'i phyi snang snod bcud phung
NK101(de)006:1614: khams skye mched rig pa gar gtad du gnas par
NK101(de)006:1615: byed pas mtha' gcig tu ngos gzung med do //
NK101(de)006:1616: tha ma sems kyi 'gro sa yang rtsis gdab med
NK101(de)006:1617: de dper na snod kyi 'jig rten rtag brtan ther
NK101(de)006:1618: zug lta bur snang ba 'di yang mthar med bdun
NK101(de)006:1619: chu gcig sogs kyis 'jig pa'i tshe stong pa chen
NK101(de)006:1620: po nam mkha'i ngang du thim zhing /
NK101(de)006:1621: nam mkha' stong pa dag la 'jig rgyu med pa bzhin /
NK101(de)006:1622: rang gi lus dang phyi rol gyi yul snang thams
NK101(de)006:1623: cad zhig cing stongs par gyur kyang sems 'di stong
NK101(de)006:1624: pa med do // sems gcig las med kyang rtsal
NK101(de)006:1625: sna tshogs su 'char bas grangs su rtsis gdab bral
NK101(de)006:1626: pa med do // ba yin / de ltar yang ka dag gi khrid gzhung las /
NK101(de)006:1627: rang rig byang chub sems 'di la sems kyis yang
NK101(de)006:1628: dang yang du ltos gzugs dang kha dog grub pa
NK101(de)006:1629: med phyogs dang ris su grub pa med mtha' dang
NK101(de)006:1630: dbus su grub pa med byung sa gnas sa 'gro
NK101(de)006:1631: sa med / stong pa cir yang ma grub pa
NK101(de)006:1632: gsal la dngas pa 'di mthong na rang ngo rang
NK101(de)006:1633: gis shes pa yin zhes gsungs /
NK101(de)006:1634: de lta bu'i sems kyi ngo bo de gsal stong
NK101(de)006:1635: snang stong rig stong dbyer med gsal le sing nge
NK101(de)006:1636: hrig ge yer re spros pa'i mtha' dang bral ba
NK101(de)006:1637: de / ngo bo stong pa chos sku /
NK101(de)006:1638: de'i rang mdangs rang bzhin gsal ba longs sku /
NK101(de)006:1639: thugs rje cir yang ma 'gags pa sprul sku ste
NK101(de)006:1640: sku gsum rang chas su grub pa de la zhen
NK101(de)006:1641: chags dang phyogs gcig tu 'dzin pa 'khrul pa yin
NK101(de)006:1642: pas rig pa bcos med rang shar rang grol 'dzin
NK101(de)006:1643: med kyi ngo bor ltos shig ces ngo sprod pa
NK101(de)006:1644: dang de bzhin du lus sems kyang dang por sems
NK101(de)006:1645: dang de las lus grub cing snang ba yang sems
NK101(de)006:1646: kyi rtsal snang chu dang chu lbur lta bu yin
NK101(de)006:1647: par gsungs pas mdor na slob ma'i dri ba dang
NK101(de)006:1648: rgyud tshod bstun nas ngo sprad do //
NK101(de)006:1649: 'di la spros na bshad gzhi yangs pas mtha' gcod
NK101(de)006:1650: dang rgyas bshad mang du 'byung yang 'di tsam gyis
NK101(de)006:1652: skabs 'dir gong gi 'phros su rtsa ba las /
NK101(de)006:1653: de las logs su zhi dang khro bo sogs /
NK101(de)006:1654: sangs rgyas yar la 'tshol ba'i re ba dang /
NK101(de)006:1655: mar la ngan song 'khor bar lhung dogs pa'i /
NK101(de)006:1656: re dwogs dang bral bar do rnams gsum gcod /
NK101(de)006:1657: 'khor 'das shan phyed bem rig mgo ltag phyed /
NK101(de)006:1658: gzung 'dzin rang grol 'od gsal ma bu 'phrad /
NK101(de)006:1659: rang rig ngo bo ma bcos thod 'phreng rtsal /
NK101(de)006:1660: zhes pa'i dgongs don la thar thug khrid yig gi /
NK101(de)006:1661: zin bris yang tig gces sgron gsal byed 'di /
NK101(de)006:1662: rig 'dzin brgyud pa'i gsung rgyun ma nyams par /
NK101(de)006:1663: bka' gter snyan brgyud 'dzin pa'i ldum bu ba /
NK101(de)006:1664: 'phrin las rab rgyas gang des bris pa la /
NK101(de)006:1665: nongs pa mchis na chos srung kun la bshags /
NK101(de)006:1666: dge 'dis kun bzang gdod ma'i sa thob shog /
NK101(de)006:1667: ces don bsdus te bshad cing /
NK101(de)006:1668: khrid gzhung las ngo sprod dngos gzhi la don gsum gyi /
NK101(de)006:1669: dang po nam mkha' la phyag mdzub gtad de ngo sprad pa dang /
NK101(de)006:1670: gnyis pa man shel la lta stangs gtad de ngo
NK101(de)006:1671: sprad pa gsum pa slob bu'i snying gar phyag mdzub
NK101(de)006:1672: gtad nas ngo sprad pa ste gsum du gsungs pa'i
NK101(de)006:1674: gu ru'i sku chos gos dang mnyen zhu gsol ba
NK101(de)006:1675: rdo rje'i skyil krung can phyag g.yas rdo rje thugs
NK101(de)006:1676: kar sdigs mdzub kyis 'dzin cing g.yon phyag mdzub dang
NK101(de)006:1677: lta stangs nam mkha' la gtad pa zhig bris pa
NK101(de)006:1678: ltar dpe rgyun du yang yod cing /
NK101(de)006:1680: phyi rabs nga yi rjes nas 'jug pa rnams ngo
NK101(de)006:1681: sprod kyi skabs su bla mas phyag rgya 'di lta
NK101(de)006:1682: bur ston cig slob bus bla ma pad+ma 'byung gnas
NK101(de)006:1683: nga nyid dngos su mos pas chos nyid kyi don
NK101(de)006:1684: rtse gcig tu rtogs shig nga'i thugs kyi bcud rtsol
NK101(de)006:1686: zhes gsungs pas spro na de ltar bya zhing gzhan du dmigs pa tsam gyis 'thus par sems so //
NK101(de)006:1688: bla mas g.yon pa'i sdigs mdzub nam mkhar gtad la /
NK101(de)006:1690: rigs kyi bu snang srid 'khor 'das kyi chos thams
NK101(de)006:1691: cad ji ltar snang yang don la yod ma myong
NK101(de)006:1692: ba cig yin zhes sogs khrid gzhung ltar ngo sprod
NK101(de)006:1693: bya dgos pa'i rgyas bshad ni khrid gzhung rim par
NK101(de)006:1694: klog cing don legs par 'grol dgos pas 'dir tshig
NK101(de)006:1695: don mdor bsdus te bshad na snang srid 'khor 'das
NK101(de)006:1696: kyi chos thams cad ji ltar snang yang don la
NK101(de)006:1698: de yang brjod bral yin pas kha nang du bltas
NK101(de)006:1699: te rang gi sems la bltas pas dang por byung
NK101(de)006:1701: bar du 'dir gnas dngos po dang mtshan mar ma grub pa /
NK101(de)006:1702: tha ma 'gro sa dang 'gro rgyu 'gag pa med pa zhig yin /
NK101(de)006:1703: de bas na 'jig rten gyi sdug bsngal lam du
NK101(de)006:1704: slong ba dang skye rga na 'chi bzhir mi 'jigs
NK101(de)006:1705: pa'i gdengs dgos pas de la bar do rnam pa
NK101(de)006:1707: de lta bu'i bar do la yang rnam pa bzhi dang drug tu dbye ba yod kyang /
NK101(de)006:1708: 'dir gsum du bsdus te srid pa bar do dang /
NK101(de)006:1709: rmi lam gyi bar do dang /
NK101(de)006:1710: skye 'chi'i bar do dang gsum du byas pa'i dang po srid pa'i bar do ni /
NK101(de)006:1711: thog mar 'khrul nas mthar 'khrul pa ma dag gi
NK101(de)006:1712: bar du 'khor bar skye 'chi dang sdug bsngal rgyun
NK101(de)006:1713: mi chad par spyod cing myong bas na srid pa
NK101(de)006:1716: sems nyid phyin ci ma log pa'i don ma rtogs
NK101(de)006:1717: na 'dus byas kyi dge rtsa ji tsam byas kyang
NK101(de)006:1718: dge 'bras des skye ba 'ga' zhig ngan song du
NK101(de)006:1719: mi 'gro yang / mthar dge ba'i stegs de nam
NK101(de)006:1720: zad pa na slar yang ngan song du lhungs te
NK101(de)006:1721: sdug bsngal las mi thar bas /
NK101(de)006:1722: 'dus byas kyi dge bas phyes pa la rta rnga
NK101(de)006:1723: nyag ma gcig tsam gyis nyer mi 'gro zhing 'khor
NK101(de)006:1724: ba las mi 'phags pa yin gsung /
NK101(de)006:1725: de'i rgyu mtshan ni gnyis pa rmi lam bar do'i dpes bstan te /
NK101(de)006:1726: gnyid du song dus kyi rmi lam du bde sdug
NK101(de)006:1727: ci rmis kyang lus ngag gnyis la ma rmis te
NK101(de)006:1728: sems kho na la rmis pa bzhin du 'chi ba'i
NK101(de)006:1730: bzang ngan thams cad sems la smin par 'gyur bas
NK101(de)006:1731: da lta rang sems ma bcos par bzhag pas bde
NK101(de)006:1732: sdug gi rnam rtog ji ltar shar yang rang byung
NK101(de)006:1733: chos skur ngo shes par 'gyur ro //
NK101(de)006:1734: gsum pa skye 'chi'i bar do ni /
NK101(de)006:1735: skyes nas ma shi'i bar der /
NK101(de)006:1736: skye ba 'dir gtan gyi so rnam bya dgos pas snying rus bskyed dgos shing /
NK101(de)006:1737: tshe 'dir bla ma dam pa dang gdam ngag zab
NK101(de)006:1738: mo 'phrad cing snyis su blangs na bar do chod
NK101(de)006:1739: cing / des rnal 'byor pa'i lus rgya yang chod par 'gyur ro //
NK101(de)006:1740: de ltar bar do rnam gsum gcod pa la man ngag tshig gsum ste /
NK101(de)006:1741: dang po 'khor 'das gcig tu bsre ba /
NK101(de)006:1742: gnyis pa bem rig mgo ltag dbye ba /
NK101(de)006:1743: gsum pa sangs rgyas dang sems can gyi 'brel thag bcad pa sde gsum las /
NK101(de)006:1744: dang po 'khor 'das gcig tu bsre ba ni /
NK101(de)006:1745: rang sems rkyen gyis ma bslad par rang sar bzhag pas /
NK101(de)006:1746: gnas lugs gzhi nas stong pa /
NK101(de)006:1748: rang bzhin gyis gsal ba 'di ngo shes par bya /
NK101(de)006:1749: de yang thog ma nas bcos pa ma yin /
NK101(de)006:1750: rang bzhin du gnas pa yin te /
NK101(de)006:1751: sangs rgyas rnams kyi thugs gnyis med kyi ye shes /
NK101(de)006:1752: sems can gyi rig pa byang chub kyi sems /
NK101(de)006:1753: rang gi rig pa ma bcos pa sogs tha dad
NK101(de)006:1754: ma yin pa gcig tu grub pa dbyer med tha
NK101(de)006:1756: rang rig rang dag rang gsal rnam rtog gis ma
NK101(de)006:1757: bslad pa de la ma yengs par yun ring du
NK101(de)006:1758: goms su bcug pas ngo bo bcos med kyi ngang
NK101(de)006:1759: du gnas shing gsal ba'i dus 'khor 'das gnyis gcig
NK101(de)006:1761: de ltar rtogs pa gdengs dang ldan pas yar sangs rgyas la re ba med /
NK101(de)006:1762: chos dang sems su 'dres pas bcos med kyi rig
NK101(de)006:1763: pa rang lugs gnyug ma'i ngang la gnas pas mar
NK101(de)006:1764: ngan song du lhung ba'i dwogs pa med pas 'khor
NK101(de)006:1766: gnyis pa bem rig mgo ltag dbye ba ni /
NK101(de)006:1767: sems kyi rten lus yin kyang /
NK101(de)006:1768: rig pa gnas lugs stong gsal du gnas pa'i phyi'i
NK101(de)006:1769: snang yul dgra gnyen longs spyod gang snang yang 'dzin
NK101(de)006:1770: pa med pas snang ba rang sar stongs /
NK101(de)006:1771: bar du rang gi lus kyang 'dzin med kyi lus yod du mi tshor /
NK101(de)006:1772: nang sems kyang 'dzin med rnam rtog rang sar zhi /
NK101(de)006:1773: gang la yang 'dzin zhen med pa de'i dus chos
NK101(de)006:1774: nyid kyi rig pa la rgyun chad med pas lus
NK101(de)006:1775: mir 'dug kyang sems sangs rgyas dang dgongs pa mnyams
NK101(de)006:1776: / bem po la gces 'dzin med par rig pa
NK101(de)006:1777: rang gsal du gnas pas bem rig mgo stag phyed
NK101(de)006:1778: / pa'o // gsum pa sangs rgyas dang sems can 'brel thag bcad pa ni /
NK101(de)006:1779: sems stong pa ma bcos pa de la sangs rgyas dang sems can du ma grub /
NK101(de)006:1780: de ltar nyams su blangs pas thag chod yid ches
NK101(de)006:1781: kyi gdengs rnyed cing don rtogs pas 'khor ba'i sdug
NK101(de)006:1782: bsngal dang skye 'chi la nyam nga med /
NK101(de)006:1783: 'chi dus lus 'pho ngag 'gags kyang rig pa rang sar gnas /
NK101(de)006:1784: rig stong 'dres pa de la phyi rol gyi rkyen gyi mi gnod /
NK101(de)006:1785: 'khor ba'i gdos thag chod pas rigs drug tu skye ba'i rgyu ma rnyed /
NK101(de)006:1786: rnam rtog gi rol brgya rig pa skad cig ma'i 'og tu tshud /
NK101(de)006:1787: chos nyid stong gsal dngas pa la nyon mongs pa'i dug ro ldang mi srid /
NK101(de)006:1788: las kyi rnam smin zad pas sdig pa phyags mas btab /
NK101(de)006:1789: lus la blang sa med pas ngan song gi sgo bcad /
NK101(de)006:1790: snang srid sems su shes pas dmyal ba gtan nas sprugs /
NK101(de)006:1791: man ngag 'di ltar nyams su len pa'i gang zag la 'chi bas mi 'jigs /
NK101(de)006:1792: tshe gcig gis gtan 'dun grub 'khor 'das gnyis med
NK101(de)006:1793: kyi man ngag tshig gsum gyis skye 'chi la zlo
NK101(de)006:1794: ba'i man ngag gsang sngags kyi bseb lam zab mo
NK101(de)006:1795: yin pas nyams su long zhig gsungs so //
NK101(de)006:1796: gnyis pa man shel la lta stangs bstad de ngo sprad pa ni man shel bstan la /
NK101(de)006:1797: rang rig byang chub kyi sems 'di la sems kyi
NK101(de)006:1798: bltas pa'i tshe gzugs dang kha dog phyogs ris mtha'
NK101(de)006:1799: dbus su ma grub pas byung gnas 'gro gsum thams
NK101(de)006:1800: cad stong pa cir yang ma grub /
NK101(de)006:1801: phyogs zhen dang bral bar 'dug pa stong pa de
NK101(de)006:1802: yang ngo bo nyid med pa ma yin te gsal
NK101(de)006:1803: la dngas pa man shel lta bu 'di mthong ngam
NK101(de)006:1804: / ma mthong na 'jig rten gyi zas nor dgra
NK101(de)006:1805: gnyen gyi 'dzin pa thams cad gos hrul bor bzhin
NK101(de)006:1806: bskyur lus la gces par gzung yang shing sdong gog
NK101(de)006:1807: po'i bya tshang dang 'dra bas gces 'dzin bskyur /
NK101(de)006:1808: tshong pa bde ba'i lam 'tshol ba ltar lus ngag
NK101(de)006:1809: yid gsum mnyam par zhog la chos nyid kyi lam
NK101(de)006:1810: tshol / sgeg mo me long la blta ba ltar sems la yang yang ltos /
NK101(de)006:1811: rkun ma grong nas 'byung bas nang du rtsad chod /
NK101(de)006:1812: dgra ngo shes dus sgrol la phyin chad sgo bsdoms shes pa glod la nyol /
NK101(de)006:1813: sems ma bcos pa'i ngang la blta ba ni rang ngo rang gis shes pa yin /
NK101(de)006:1814: chos nyid kyi don go zhing mthong ba yin /
NK101(de)006:1816: shes bya'i sgro 'dogs chod pa yin /
NK101(de)006:1817: rang sems dngos por ma grub pa rang byung rang
NK101(de)006:1818: gnas rtag chad kyi mtha' las 'das pas sangs rgyas
NK101(de)006:1819: gzhan nas btsal mi dgos te gzung 'dzin gyi rtog
NK101(de)006:1820: pa sangs nas ma bcos pa'i ye shes rgyas /
NK101(de)006:1821: ngan 'gror 'gro ba'i rgyu ngan pa dor rgyu med pas rig pa rang sar dag /
NK101(de)006:1822: chos la byed mkhan dang bya rgyu med pas chos nyid rang gsal du gsal /
NK101(de)006:1823: lta ba rang la yod pas gzhan nas btsal du
NK101(de)006:1824: med pa de'i don rtogs nas nyams su len pa'i
NK101(de)006:1825: tshe / rang lus ri bo dgon pa'i gnas /
NK101(de)006:1826: phyi'i snang ba gang shar thams cad snang stong rang
NK101(de)006:1827: byung rang zhi spros pa'i mtha' dang bral bar bzhag
NK101(de)006:1828: / de ltar shes pas snang ba grogs su shar /
NK101(de)006:1829: gzung 'dzin rang sar dag ci byung lam du 'khyer bas nyams len bde /
NK101(de)006:1830: 'gyu dran rang sar dag cing lam du lhongs /
NK101(de)006:1831: de'i tshe bsgom bya bsgom byed thams cad grogs su shar bas nyams la gsal 'grib med /
NK101(de)006:1832: chos nyid dang ye shes rgyun chad med spyod pa la yangs dog med /
NK101(de)006:1834: rgyun chad dang phyogs ris med /
NK101(de)006:1835: mi 'gyur ba'i brtan pa thob pas de ltar nyams su long /
NK101(de)006:1836: man ngag zab mo 'di sangs rgyas thams cad kyi thugs gsang brtol ba yin pas /
NK101(de)006:1837: mthong bltas reg chog yin pa'i phyir na so rgan
NK101(de)006:1838: gzhon dbang po rno rtul shes rab che chung skye
NK101(de)006:1839: ba mtho dman med pas ci'i phyir na thams cad
NK101(de)006:1841: sems med pa'i sems can mi srid pas bya ba
NK101(de)006:1842: thams cad byis pa'i rtsed mo'am srin bu'i kha chus
NK101(de)006:1843: rang bcings pa dang 'dra ba rang sdug rang gis
NK101(de)006:1845: thams cad rgyangs bskyur 'dzin zhen med par bzhag pas
NK101(de)006:1846: rig pa gsal stong du yer re 'byung bas de
NK101(de)006:1847: la goms pas bem rig bral dus ye shes chos
NK101(de)006:1848: kyi sku dang 'du 'bral med pas shin tu zab
NK101(de)006:1849: / de la brtan pa thob kyi bar du dgos pa'i man ngag brgyad yod pas /
NK101(de)006:1850: 'chi ba bsams shing mi rtag pa dran par bya
NK101(de)006:1851: zhing tshe la sdod long med pas brtson 'grus bskyed
NK101(de)006:1852: / brtson 'grus grogs las 'byung bas grub thob gong ma'i rnam thar soms /
NK101(de)006:1853: long gtam 'chal gtam spongs la gcig pur sdod /
NK101(de)006:1854: nye 'brel dang bu tshas 'ching bas 'brel thag chod /
NK101(de)006:1855: zas nor sdug bsngal yin pas gang byung zas su zo /
NK101(de)006:1856: las ngan grogs kyis slob pas sdig spyod kyi grogs ma sten /
NK101(de)006:1857: tshig 'di dpe tsam yin pas don la cher gyis bsgoms /
NK101(de)006:1858: ma yengs lam sna yin pas dran pa'i rtsis gzung /
NK101(de)006:1859: zhes gsungs pa ltar ngo sprad do //
NK101(de)006:1860: gsum pa slob bu'i snying gar sdigs mdzub bstad nas ngo sprad pa ni /
NK101(de)006:1862: rigs kyi bu lus tsog pur zhog la drang por srongs /
NK101(de)006:1863: sems khong glod la dar cig zhog ces gsungs pa ltar brjod la tshig don ngo sprad pa ni /
NK101(de)006:1864: sangs rgyas kyi thugs dang sems can gyi sems la khyad par ci yod snyam na /
NK101(de)006:1865: rang sems skad cig la 'di'i don rtogs dang ma
NK101(de)006:1866: rtogs kyi khyad yin pas ma rtogs pas ma rig
NK101(de)006:1867: 'khrul pa byung bas dug lnga sna tshogs su shar
NK101(de)006:1869: sangs rgyas kyi rgyu rang la yod pa de ngo ma shes /
NK101(de)006:1870: de ltar sangs rgyas kyi rgyu sems can thams cad
NK101(de)006:1871: la yod cing sgos dal 'byor gyi mi la che
NK101(de)006:1872: chung mtho dman med par yod /
NK101(de)006:1873: de rtogs byed kyi thabs su sangs rgyas rnams kyis
NK101(de)006:1874: chos sgo brgyad khri bzhi stong gsungs kyang bsdu na
NK101(de)006:1877: phyi gzung yul dag pas snang ba rang sar grol
NK101(de)006:1878: nang 'dzin sems dag pas rig pa rang sar grol
NK101(de)006:1879: bar du 'od gsal ma bu 'phrod pas rang ngo
NK101(de)006:1880: rang gis shes pa'o de'i don cung zhig bkrol na
NK101(de)006:1881: / phyi gzung yul dag pa ni /
NK101(de)006:1882: rang sems rnam rtog gis ma bslad pa rang gsal
NK101(de)006:1883: du bzhag pas phyi rol bde sdug gi yul snang
NK101(de)006:1884: la 'dzin pa ma zhugs pas snang ba ji ltar
NK101(de)006:1885: shar yang bden pa dang dngos por ma grub cing
NK101(de)006:1886: / bdag 'dzin gyi blo dag pas phyi gzung yul dag pa bya ba yin /
NK101(de)006:1887: gzung yul dag pa zhes med par 'gro ba ma
NK101(de)006:1888: yin te zhen 'dzin med pas me long gi gzugs
NK101(de)006:1889: brnyan bden par ma grub pa ltar snang yul 'di
NK101(de)006:1890: rmi lam sgyu ma byis pa'i rtsed mo'am /
NK101(de)006:1891: bar snang gi 'ja' tshon lta bu'o //
NK101(de)006:1893: sems la rnam rtog dug lnga gang skyes kyang /
NK101(de)006:1894: gang shar blos ma gzung bar rgyang bskyur cham bzhag /
NK101(de)006:1895: dug gi me tog bkrag che yang nor du mi 'dzin pa ltar /
NK101(de)006:1896: rnam rtog gi rjes su mi 'breng bar ngo bo
NK101(de)006:1897: la blta zhing lhod kyis glod pas rang grol du
NK101(de)006:1898: 'gro / 'gyu byed kyi rkyen gyis mi gos /
NK101(de)006:1899: 'dzin sems dag pa zhes bem po sa rdo ltar 'gro ba ma yin te /
NK101(de)006:1900: rig pa la rtog pa'i dri ma mi 'jog pa ste /
NK101(de)006:1901: rin po che gser gling du sa rdo gzhan med
NK101(de)006:1902: pa ltar dran rig rang grol du shes pas rnam
NK101(de)006:1903: rtog gi ming yang med pa'o //
NK101(de)006:1904: bar du 'od gsal ma bu 'phrod pa ni /
NK101(de)006:1905: de ltar nyams su blangs pas /
NK101(de)006:1906: rang gi shes rig dri med gsal le sing nge
NK101(de)006:1907: chos nyid rang byung gi ye shes bde gsal mi
NK101(de)006:1908: rtog pa zhen 'dzin gyi ma bslad pa'i nyams shig
NK101(de)006:1909: 'char ba de sangs rgyas kyii dgongs pa yin pas
NK101(de)006:1910: rang ngo rang shes de dran pas rgyun chags su
NK101(de)006:1911: gzung bas / gzung 'dzin gyi rnam rtog rang sar grol /
NK101(de)006:1912: gzhi ma bcos pa'i chos nyid rtogs pa'i gdengs the
NK101(de)006:1913: tshom skyon bral du 'char ba de 'od gsal ma
NK101(de)006:1915: rang gi ma dang phrad na mar bsgom mi dgos
NK101(de)006:1916: pa bzhin du rang rig rang byung chos nyid yin
NK101(de)006:1917: par ngo shes pas 'khor ba thams cad chos nyid
NK101(de)006:1919: yang dag pa'i don yin min gyi rtog pa mi
NK101(de)006:1920: 'char bas chos thams cad la rang bzhin med pa
NK101(de)006:1921: ni ma dang rang bzhin med par shes pa de
NK101(de)006:1923: rig pa chos dbyings su ngos zin pas rang ngo
NK101(de)006:1924: rang gis shes pa bya ba yin pas de'i tshe
NK101(de)006:1925: lus mi ru snang yang sems rdo rje sems dpa'
NK101(de)006:1926: rang byung gi ye shes chen po rtogs pa yin
NK101(de)006:1927: no // gsungs pa ltar ngo sprad do //
NK101(de)006:1929: phyii ltar gzung ba'i yul snang dag pa dang nang
NK101(de)006:1930: ltar 'dzin pa'i sems nyid grol ba dang bar du
NK101(de)006:1931: 'od gsal rang ngo shes pa dang zhes gsungs pa
NK101(de)006:1932: ltar ro // de ltar ngo sprod gsum po de
NK101(de)006:1933: 'di dngos gzhi'i nyams len gal che bar 'dug pas
NK101(de)006:1934: yig tshogs la ma bltas par khrid gzhung gi don
NK101(de)006:1936: 'di yan chad nyams khrid du bskyang zhing sems ngo 'phrod nges pa bya dgos shing /
NK101(de)006:1937: rgyun gyi nyams len ni 'ga' zhig dmigs rim rnams bstar chags su bsgom pa las /
NK101(de)006:1938: dran shes kyi rtsis zin pa'i nyams len gnad du
NK101(de)006:1939: bsnun pa med par thob chos tsam byed pa ni
NK101(de)006:1940: rang gis rang bslus pa yin pas ka dag khregs
NK101(de)006:1941: chod kyi gnas lugs gtso bor bya dgos shing /
NK101(de)006:1942: de nyid lam du 'khyer thabs su /
NK101(de)006:1943: sngon 'gro gzer lnga dang bdag bskyed kyi ngang nas
NK101(de)006:1944: sum brgya nyer gcig gi bzlas pa tsam byas na
NK101(de)006:1945: skyon du mi 'gyur zhing grogs su 'gyur la /
NK101(de)006:1946: gzhan du rdo rje dkar po'i sems 'dzin sogs las
NK101(de)006:1947: dang po pa zhi gnas kyi thabs su khrid kyi
NK101(de)006:1949: thig le dkar dmar sogs gnad bzhi'i sems 'dzin ni skabs 'gar bsgoms kyang bogs che /
NK101(de)006:1950: gtso bor gnas lugs kyi don blta ba gal che zhing /
NK101(de)006:1951: de la yang rdzogs chen zang thal gyi cha lag
NK101(de)006:1952: bar do lnga'i ngo sprod las nyin mo bya ba
NK101(de)006:1953: sgom du 'gro ba la snang ba rgya yan gyi
NK101(de)006:1954: man ngag gces mtshan mo nyal bas gnyid sgom du
NK101(de)006:1955: 'gro ba la srod la dbang po gnad bsdus kyii
NK101(de)006:1956: man ngag gces nam phyed shes bya bum 'jug gi
NK101(de)006:1957: man ngag gces tho rangs ye shes rang gsal gyi
NK101(de)006:1958: man ngag gces gces pa rnam pa bzhi'i man ngag
NK101(de)006:1959: chongs mdzod ces gsungs pa'i don bsdus te bshad na
NK101(de)006:1960: / sems la rgyu rkyen gyis ma bskyed /
NK101(de)006:1961: gzhan gyis ma byas blo bur du byung ba ma yin /
NK101(de)006:1962: sems nyid 'di 'dra zhes bstan du med /
NK101(de)006:1963: ngo bo stong pa 'gyur med nam mkha' dang 'dra bas /
NK101(de)006:1964: rang snang ris med kyi snang ba gtan la dbab /
NK101(de)006:1965: phyi rol gyi yul snang sna tshogs su 'dug kyang rang snang yin /
NK101(de)006:1966: snang ba la 'dzin pa med par blta /
NK101(de)006:1967: bar du blo'i snang ba rnam rtog phra rags ci
NK101(de)006:1968: skyes ci shar thams cad gzhi rtsa dang bral bas
NK101(de)006:1970: tha ma g.yo 'gul gyi nyams snang bde gsal mi
NK101(de)006:1971: rtog pa gang byung yang chags 'dzin med pa chu
NK101(de)006:1973: snang stong gnyis po la snga phyi med pas snang
NK101(de)006:1974: ba rang snang stong pa rang stong sems nyid stong
NK101(de)006:1975: pa gnyis med bde chen gsal la ma 'dres pas
NK101(de)006:1976: 'ja' tshon lta bur rtogs tsa na /
NK101(de)006:1977: snang ba gsal la ma 'gags rig pa stong la 'dzin med /
NK101(de)006:1978: snang ba ma spangs rang grol /
NK101(de)006:1979: rnam par mi rtog pa mtshan ma rang grol chos nyid kyi don khong du chud pas /
NK101(de)006:1980: ye shes rgyun chad med pa'i man ngag 'dis rtsis zin na /
NK101(de)006:1981: nyin mo bya ba bsgom du 'gro ba snang ba rgya yan gyi man ngag yin /
NK101(de)006:1982: srod la gnyid du 'gro ba'i tshe /
NK101(de)006:1983: dbang po lnga ched du mi dgag ched du mi
NK101(de)006:1984: bsdu bar sgo lnga gsal la 'dzin med ye shes
NK101(de)006:1986: gnyid za zi'i dus kun gzhi stong pa rtsa bral
NK101(de)006:1987: gyi ngang du shes pa gsal la 'dzin med du
NK101(de)006:1988: bzhag pa'i ngang la gnyid du thum song bas bag
NK101(de)006:1989: chags ngan pa'i rmi lam mi 'byung bar gnyid dus
NK101(de)006:1990: rmi lam gyi nang du shes pa gsal le sing
NK101(de)006:1991: nge 'dzin med du 'char ba rang byung gi don
NK101(de)006:1992: la bzhag pa ni srod la dbang po ga nad
NK101(de)006:1994: nam phyed dus bum nang gi mar me rang gsal
NK101(de)006:1995: phyiir mi 'phro ba ltar rig pa nang du gsal
NK101(de)006:1996: la 'dzin med ngo bo dngas gsal mi g.yo bar
NK101(de)006:1997: bzhag pa ni nam phyed shes bya bum 'jug gi
NK101(de)006:1998: man ngag yin / tho rangs gnyid phrad sad pa'i
NK101(de)006:1999: dus su gong gi gsal la 'dzin med de gsal
NK101(de)006:2000: btab la sgo lnga gsal la ma 'gags 'dzin zhen
NK101(de)006:2001: man ngag yin / med pa / me long g.ya' dag la gzugs brnyan gsal ba ltar /
NK101(de)006:2002: chos nyid kyi don ye gsal de yang gsal du gsal stong gnyis med du sgom pa ni /
NK101(de)006:2003: tho rangs ye shes rang gsal gyi man ngag yin
NK101(de)006:2004: par gsungs pa khregs chod nyams su len pa la
NK101(de)006:2005: gal che bar snang bas de ltar nyams su blang
NK101(de)006:2006: ngo // de yang mnyam par bzhag pa'i dus rnam rtog gi 'phro 'du bkag pas mi khegs shing /
NK101(de)006:2007: rjes su yang mi 'breng bar rang babs su bzhag
NK101(de)006:2008: pa'i dran pa ma yengs pa'i ngang nas 'gyu ba
NK101(de)006:2009: phra rags sbom gsum ci shar yang ngos gzung nas
NK101(de)006:2010: ngo bo la blta ba yin pas /
NK101(de)006:2012: sngon bsu rjes gcod blo yis bcos mi gzhug 'gyu
NK101(de)006:2013: ba rang sar bzhag pas chos skur grol zhes dang
NK101(de)006:2014: / thang yig tu ngang byung rgyal mor gdams pa
NK101(de)006:2015: las lus sems ma bsgrim lhod de shig ge zhog
NK101(de)006:2016: ma gzhi stong pa nyid kyi zhi gnas su rnam
NK101(de)006:2017: rtog mthar 'ded stong skor rem la gyis nyams la
NK101(de)006:2018: 'di 'byung bya ba med de 'byung bsgom la ma
NK101(de)006:2019: zhen yang nas yang du bshig bzang rtog ngan rtog
NK101(de)006:2020: gang shar cer cer ltos zhes dang /
NK101(de)006:2021: ka dag gi khrid yig snying po bcud bsdus lam gyi gnad khrid las /
NK101(de)006:2022: rig pa byang chub sems 'di la rnam rtog 'khrul
NK101(de)006:2023: pas ma bslad par rang gsal so mar bzhag pa
NK101(de)006:2024: yis yul la 'dzin pa ma zhugs te gang ltar
NK101(de)006:2025: shar yang 'dzin pa med bdag tu 'dzin pa'i blo
NK101(de)006:2026: ma zhugs gang shar 'dzin pa med pa de gzung
NK101(de)006:2027: ba'i yul snang dag pa yin sems la dug lnga
NK101(de)006:2028: gang skyes kyang gang dran blo yis ma gzung bas
NK101(de)006:2029: 'gyu ba rang sar grol ba yin de ltar nyams
NK101(de)006:2030: su blangs pa yis rang rig dri ma med pa
NK101(de)006:2031: la gsal le hrig ge rang byung ste rgyud la
NK101(de)006:2032: nyams su longs pa'i tshe zhen 'dzin blo yis ma
NK101(de)006:2033: bslad pa'i bde gsal mi rtog nyams shig 'char gzhan
NK101(de)006:2034: nas 'char ba ma yin te rang ngo rang gis
NK101(de)006:2035: shes pa yin sangs rgyas dgongs pa mthar thug yin
NK101(de)006:2036: zhes gsungs pa don 'dus shing go sla bar 'dug
NK101(de)006:2038: gzhan du skabs 'dir mdo rgyud spyi dang rang lugs
NK101(de)006:2039: kyi lung mang du mchis kyang yi ger 'jigs te
NK101(de)006:2040: ma bkod cing 'di tsam gyis don go bar sems
NK101(de)006:2041: so // deng sang khrid zhus rlom kha cig don
NK101(de)006:2042: gyi snying po dor zhing dmigs rim rnams thar chags
NK101(de)006:2043: su sgom pa gtso bor byas pas rgyud thog tu
NK101(de)006:2044: nyams len mi khel bar chos dang gang zag so
NK101(de)006:2045: sor lus pa lta bu dang /
NK101(de)006:2046: gnas lugs kyi ro ma myong bas sems tha mal
NK101(de)006:2047: du lus pa'i 'gyu ba phra rags rtsad ma chod
NK101(de)006:2048: par 'og 'gyu rgya 'byams la gnas par 'khrul ba
NK101(de)006:2049: dang / rnam rtog spang byar 'khrul te nan gyis
NK101(de)006:2050: 'gegs pa sogs shor gol gyi dbang du 'gro ba
NK101(de)006:2051: dang / mthong bas / gtso bor sems kyi bzhag thabs kho na gal che ba'i phyir /
NK101(de)006:2052: thog mar blo mas ngo sprad pa'i don ma 'khrul
NK101(de)006:2053: bar nyams su blang zhing mnyam rjes dbyer med du
NK101(de)006:2054: ma gyur bar nyams myong dang bstun pa'i gegs sel
NK101(de)006:2056: skabs 'dir byang gter rdzogs chen rang gi gegs sel
NK101(de)006:2057: nor bu'i bang mdzod gces par snang bas rgyud tshod
NK101(de)006:2058: dang bstun pa'i nyams su len par mdzod cig /
NK101(de)006:2059: de ltar yang tig gces pa'i sgron me yi /
NK101(de)006:2060: zin bris gzhung don rab gsal zhes bya ba /
NK101(de)006:2061: 'khor lo'i mgon po gter chen chos kyi rgyal /
NK101(de)006:2062: 'gyur med rdo rje'i bka' yis bskul ba'i ngor /
NK101(de)006:2063: dge slong rgan po pad+ma 'phrin las kyis /
NK101(de)006:2064: gzhung don gtsor byas bla ma'i man ngag gis /
NK101(de)006:2065: legs brgyan rang gzo'i bcos bslad ma bgyis par /
NK101(de)006:2066: bris 'di mkhyen ldan rnams kyis dpyad par 'tshal /
NK101(de)006:2067: dge 'dis tshe rabs kun tu las bzang po /
NK101(de)006:2068: snga 'gyur smin grol chos kyi dga' ston gyis /
NK101(de)006:2069: khregs chod thod rgal nyams myong mthar phyin nas /
NK101(de)006:2070: kun bzang gdod ma'i mgon po mchog thob shog /
NK101(de)006:2071: de yang khrid yig 'ga' zhig tu gter gzhung gi
NK101(de)006:2072: dgongs don ma lon pa'i phyi dkyil gyi bsrung 'khor
NK101(de)006:2073: rten brten pa'i dmigs khrid rgyas par bshad cing /
NK101(de)006:2074: gzhung don rnams rang sor bzhag pa sogs 'dra min sna tshogs su bris par brten /
NK101(de)006:2075: khyab bdag bla ma rtsod bral gyi gter bton rigs
NK101(de)006:2076: 'dzin gter bdag gling pa'i bkas rtsoms shig par nan
NK101(de)006:2077: tur chen pos rtsal bar ldog par ma nus shing
NK101(de)006:2078: / rang la nyams myong dang skyes sbyangs kyi blo
NK101(de)006:2079: gros cha phra ba dang khyad par na tshod kyis
NK101(de)006:2080: gtugs shing mig kyang mi gsal ba bcas dka' tshegs
NK101(de)006:2082: bla ma'i bka' bsgrub pa'i slad dang /
NK101(de)006:2083: don gnyer can 'ga' zhig la yang phan par bsams
NK101(de)006:2084: te gtso bor gter gzhung gi khrid yig shog ser
NK101(de)006:2085: gyi bu dpe dngos la gtugs shing /
NK101(de)006:2086: zur chen rdo rje 'chang gi gsung zin bris su
NK101(de)006:2087: ka dag rang byung rang shar gyi sngon 'gror zhal
NK101(de)006:2089: de'i rgyu mtshan thugs sgrub kyi chos skor gzhan rnams gtso bor lho gser mdzod dang /
NK101(de)006:2090: dbus snying mdzod sogs su kha 'thor yang /
NK101(de)006:2091: 'di ni shar phyogs dung mdzod du ka dag gi
NK101(de)006:2092: chos skor dang lhan gcig zab gter du bzhugs pa
NK101(de)006:2093: sogs rigs mthun pas kha 'geng rnams de las bgyis
NK101(de)006:2094: shing / gzhan du rang gzo dang bsre lhad ma
NK101(de)006:2095: 'dres par thub bstan rdo rje brag gi chos smra
NK101(de)006:2096: ba'i dge slong bya bral ba pad+ma 'phrin las kyis
NK101(de)006:2097: rang la don gnyis su sleb pa sa ga zla
NK101(de)006:2098: ba'i shes phyogs kyi dmar cha'i gang ba spen pa
NK101(de)006:2099: rnar ma'i 'grub sbyor nyin rdzogs par sbyar ba'i yi
NK101(de)006:2100: ge pa ni nye gnas dge slong pad+ma phan bdes
NK101(de)006:2101: bgyis pa'i dge des 'gro kun gdod ma'i mgon po'i
NK101(de)006:2102: go 'phang thob pa'i rgyur gyur cig ka l+y+aa na
NK101(de)006:2103: shing / war+han+tu//// lam thamsacada kyi rming rdo skyabs su 'gro ba dang /
NK101(de)006:2104: theg chen byang chub mchog tu sems bskyed pa'i gzer /
NK101(de)006:2105: mthun rkyen tshogs gnyis bsags pa man+dala gyi gzer /
NK101(de)006:2106: 'gal rkyen sdig sgrib sbyongs spyir rdor sems bsgom bzlas kyi gzer /
NK101(de)006:2107: 'khor ba la nges par 'byung bar mi rtag bskul 'debs gces pa'i blo ldog rnam bzhi'i gzer /
NK101(de)006:2108: rtogs pa'i ye shes rang rgyud la 'pho ba'i thabs
